<h3 data-start="234" data-end="266">🌐 What Your Current Site is</h3>
<ul data-start="267" data-end="614">
<li data-start="267" data-end="424">
<p data-start="269" data-end="424">It’s a business website for <strong data-start="297" data-end="318">Bev’s Repair Inc.</strong>, showing services, contact info, parts listings, employment, etc. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 69px;"><a href="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" style="max-width: 69px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">bevsrepair.ca</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-start="425" data-end="614">
<p data-start="427" data-end="614">It looks like it’s built and hosted with <strong data-start="468" data-end="479">Webador</strong>, which is a website builder platform that typically requires a <strong data-start="543" data-end="564">paid subscription</strong> to remove their branding and use a custom domain.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="616" data-end="642">🔑 Things Working Well</h3>
<p data-start="643" data-end="986">✔ You have navigation to key sections like About Us, Contact, Services, Vehicles, Parts. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 69px;"><a href="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" style="max-width: 69px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">bevsrepair.ca</span></span></span></a></span></span><br data-start="769" data-end="772">
✔ Contact details and a contact form are there for customers. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 69px;"><a href="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/contact?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/contact?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" style="max-width: 69px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">bevsrepair.ca</span></span></span></a></span></span><br data-start="871" data-end="874">
✔ Your About page has good info about the business history and services. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 69px;"><a href="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/about-us?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.bevsrepair.ca/about-us?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" style="max-width: 69px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">bevsrepair.ca</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h3 data-start="988" data-end="1024">💡 Why You Might Still Be Paying</h3>
<p data-start="1025" data-end="1251">Even though you have a custom domain (<code data-start="1063" data-end="1078">bevsrepair.ca</code>), the site likely depends on a <strong data-start="1110" data-end="1134">Webador subscription</strong> behind the scenes to host it. That’s where the <strong data-start="1182" data-end="1208">monthly or yearly fees</strong> usually come in with hosted site builders.</p>
<hr data-start="1253" data-end="1256">
<h2 data-start="1258" data-end="1308">👍 How to Have a Website <em data-start="1286" data-end="1308">Without Monthly Fees</em></h2>
<p data-start="1310" data-end="1411">If your goal is to keep the <strong data-start="1338" data-end="1355">custom domain</strong> but not pay a monthly hosting fee, consider this setup:</p>
<h3 data-start="1413" data-end="1465">⚙️ Step-by-Step Alternative (No Monthly Hosting)</h3>
<ol data-start="1466" data-end="1725">
<li data-start="1466" data-end="1550">
<p data-start="1469" data-end="1550"><strong data-start="1469" data-end="1489">Keep your domain</strong> (<code data-start="1491" data-end="1506">bevsrepair.ca</code>) — that still costs around ~$15–$25/year.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1551" data-end="1643">
<p data-start="1554" data-end="1643">Build a <strong data-start="1562" data-end="1580">static website</strong> (simple HTML/CSS) — minimal design like your current layout.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1644" data-end="1725">
<p data-start="1647" data-end="1670">Host it for free using:</p>
<ul data-start="1674" data-end="1725">
<li data-start="1674" data-end="1692">
<p data-start="1676" data-end="1692"><strong data-start="1676" data-end="1692">GitHub Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1696" data-end="1709">
<p data-start="1698" data-end="1709"><strong data-start="1698" data-end="1709">Netlify</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1713" data-end="1725">
<p data-start="1715" data-end="1725"><strong data-start="1715" data-end="1725">Vercel</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1727" data-end="1924">These free hosts will serve your site (show your pages online) without any monthly fee.<br data-start="1814" data-end="1817">
You just <strong data-start="1826" data-end="1847">point your domain</strong> from your domain registrar to the free hosting source — once — and it works.</p>
<hr data-start="1926" data-end="1929">
<h2 data-start="1931" data-end="1974">👍 Benefits of Switching to Free Hosting</h2>
<p data-start="1975" data-end="2156">✨ No hosting subscription every month/year (just domain renewal)<br data-start="2039" data-end="2042">
✨ You fully control the content<br data-start="2073" data-end="2076">
✨ No third-party branding or forced templates<br data-start="2121" data-end="2124">
✨ Faster loading for customers</p>
<hr data-start="2158" data-end="2161">
<h2 data-start="2163" data-end="2185">🤝 If You Want Help</h2>
<p data-start="2186" data-end="2238">I can absolutely help you with the next steps, like:</p>
<ul data-start="2239" data-end="2373">
<li data-start="2239" data-end="2294">
<p data-start="2241" data-end="2294">Creating a simple static version of your current site</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2295" data-end="2336">
<p data-start="2297" data-end="2336">Showing how to upload it to a free host</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2337" data-end="2373">
<p data-start="2339" data-end="2373">Explaining how to link your domain</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2375" data-end="2480">Just let me know what you’d like to focus on first — the design, the hosting setup, or something else! 😊</p>
