<p data-start="97" data-end="309">This example is a <strong data-start="115" data-end="149">static site (fast + looks pro)</strong>, hosted free on Netlify, but you can <strong data-start="187" data-end="232">edit pages/photos in a simple admin panel</strong> (Decap/Netlify CMS). No monthly site-builder fees — just your yearly domain.</p>
<hr data-start="311" data-end="314">
<h2 data-start="316" data-end="347">1) What the build looks like</h2>
<h3 data-start="349" data-end="358">Pages</h3>
<ul data-start="359" data-end="463">
<li data-start="359" data-end="407">
<p data-start="361" data-end="407"><strong data-start="361" data-end="369">Home</strong> (hero + call/text + hours + services)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="408" data-end="422">
<p data-start="410" data-end="422"><strong data-start="410" data-end="422">Services</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="423" data-end="436">
<p data-start="425" data-end="436"><strong data-start="425" data-end="436">Gallery</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="437" data-end="463">
<p data-start="439" data-end="463"><strong data-start="439" data-end="450">Contact</strong> (map + form)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="465" data-end="484">Easy management</h3>
<ul data-start="485" data-end="608">
<li data-start="485" data-end="508">
<p data-start="487" data-end="508">You log into <code data-start="500" data-end="508">/admin</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="509" data-end="554">
<p data-start="511" data-end="554">Edit text like “Hours”, “Services”, “About”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="555" data-end="575">
<p data-start="557" data-end="575">Add gallery photos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="576" data-end="608">
<p data-start="578" data-end="608">Click “Publish” → site updates</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="610" data-end="613">
<h2 data-start="615" data-end="649">2) Folder structure (copy this)</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="651" data-end="907"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>bevs-site/</span><br><span>  index.html</span><br><span>  services.html</span><br><span>  gallery.html</span><br><span>  contact.html</span><br><span>  assets/</span><br><span>    css/styles.css</span><br><span>    js/site.js</span><br><span>    img/   (your photos + logo)</span><br><span>  content/</span><br><span>    settings.json</span><br><span>    services.json</span><br><span>    gallery.json</span><br><span>  admin/</span><br><span>    index.html</span><br><span>    config.yml</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="909" data-end="912">
