<h2 data-start="7436" data-end="7475">4) The “easy management” admin panel</h2>
<h3 data-start="7477" data-end="7499"><code data-start="7481" data-end="7499">admin/index.html</code></h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="7500" data-end="7777"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="Toggle view" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼf">&lt;!doctype html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;meta</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">charset</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"utf-8"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼo">/&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;meta</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"viewport"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">content</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"width=device-width,initial-scale=1"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼo">/&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;title&gt;</span><span>Site Admin</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;script</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">src</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"https://unpkg.com/decap-cms@^3.0.0/dist/decap-cms.js"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;body&gt;&lt;/body&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/html&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="7779" data-end="7829"><code data-start="7783" data-end="7801">admin/config.yml</code> (defines what you can edit)</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="7830" data-end="9453"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>YAML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>backend:</span><br><span>  name: git-gateway</span><br><span>  branch: main</span><br><br><span>media_folder: </span><span class="ͼk">"assets/img"</span><br><span>public_folder: </span><span class="ͼk">"/assets/img"</span><br><br><span>collections:</span><br><span>  - name: </span><span class="ͼk">"content"</span><br><span>    label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Site Content"</span><br><span>    files:</span><br><span>      - label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Settings"</span><br><span>        name: </span><span class="ͼk">"settings"</span><br><span>        file: </span><span class="ͼk">"content/settings.json"</span><br><span>        format: </span><span class="ͼk">"json"</span><br><span>        fields:</span><br><span>          - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Hero Title"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"heroTitle"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>          - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Hero Subtitle"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"heroSubtitle"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"text"</span><span> }</span><br><span>          - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Phone"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"phone"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>          - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Email"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"email"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>          - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Address"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"address"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>          - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"City"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"city"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>          - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Maps URL"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"mapsUrl"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>          - label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Hours"</span><br><span>            name: </span><span class="ͼk">"hours"</span><br><span>            widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"object"</span><br><span>            fields:</span><br><span>              - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Mon"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"Mon"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>              - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Tue"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"Tue"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>              - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Wed"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"Wed"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>              - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Thu"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"Thu"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>              - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Fri"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"Fri"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>              - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Sat"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"Sat"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><span>              - { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Sun"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"Sun"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span><br><br><span>      - label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Services"</span><br><span>        name: </span><span class="ͼk">"services"</span><br><span>        file: </span><span class="ͼk">"content/services.json"</span><br><span>        format: </span><span class="ͼk">"json"</span><br><span>        fields:</span><br><span>          - label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Service Items"</span><br><span>            name: </span><span class="ͼk">"items"</span><br><span>            widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"list"</span><br><span>            field: { label: </span><span class="ͼk">"Item"</span><span>, name: </span><span class="ͼk">"item"</span><span>, widget: </span><span class="ͼk">"string"</span><span> }</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="9455" data-end="9458">
<h2 data-start="9460" data-end="9499">5) How you publish this (high level)</h2>
<ol data-start="9500" data-end="9726">
<li data-start="9500" data-end="9557">
<p data-start="9503" data-end="9557">Put these files in a folder and upload to <strong data-start="9545" data-end="9555">GitHub</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="9558" data-end="9607">
<p data-start="9561" data-end="9607">Connect GitHub to <strong data-start="9579" data-end="9590">Netlify</strong> (free hosting)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="9608" data-end="9684">
<p data-start="9611" data-end="9684">Turn on <strong data-start="9619" data-end="9645">Identity + Git Gateway</strong> in Netlify (so <code data-start="9661" data-end="9669">/admin</code> login works)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="9685" data-end="9726">
<p data-start="9688" data-end="9726">Point <strong data-start="9694" data-end="9711">bevsrepair.ca</strong> DNS to Netlify</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="9728" data-end="9731">
<p data-start="9733" data-end="9824">If you want, I can tailor this example to match what you already have on <strong data-start="9806" data-end="9823">bevsrepair.ca</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="9825" data-end="9952">
<li data-start="9825" data-end="9842">
<p data-start="9827" data-end="9842">Same menu items</p>
</li>
<li data-start="9843" data-end="9868">
<p data-start="9845" data-end="9868">Your real services list</p>
</li>
<li data-start="9869" data-end="9902">
<p data-start="9871" data-end="9902">Photos + a nicer gallery layout</p>
</li>
<li data-start="9903" data-end="9952">
<p data-start="9905" data-end="9952">Click-to-call + click-for-directions for mobile</p>
</li>
</ul>
