s focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="a3589cc1-6f37-4487-bef5-8ec2add20568" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="43">Love it — let’s move this forward properly.</p>
<p data-start="45" data-end="139">I’m going to build you a <strong data-start="70" data-end="125">complete, professional Bev’s Repair website package</strong> that you can:</p>
<ul data-start="141" data-end="279">
<li data-start="141" data-end="170">
<p data-start="143" data-end="170">Upload directly to GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-start="171" data-end="193">
<p data-start="173" data-end="193">Connect to Netlify</p>
</li>
<li data-start="194" data-end="227">
<p data-start="196" data-end="227">Manage through an admin login</p>
</li>
<li data-start="228" data-end="254">
<p data-start="230" data-end="254">Point bevsrepair.ca to</p>
</li>
<li data-start="255" data-end="279">
<p data-start="257" data-end="279">Pay $0/month hosting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="281" data-end="284">
<h1 data-start="286" data-end="315">✅ What I’m Building For You</h1>
<h3 data-start="317" data-end="327">Pages:</h3>
<ul data-start="328" data-end="375">
<li data-start="328" data-end="334">
<p data-start="330" data-end="334">Home</p>
</li>
<li data-start="335" data-end="345">
<p data-start="337" data-end="345">Services</p>
</li>
<li data-start="346" data-end="355">
<p data-start="348" data-end="355">Gallery</p>
</li>
<li data-start="356" data-end="365">
<p data-start="358" data-end="365">Reviews</p>
</li>
<li data-start="366" data-end="375">
<p data-start="368" data-end="375">Contact</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="377" data-end="390">Features:</h3>
<ul data-start="391" data-end="545">
<li data-start="391" data-end="413">
<p data-start="393" data-end="413">Click-to-call button</p>
</li>
<li data-start="414" data-end="438">
<p data-start="416" data-end="438">Google Maps directions</p>
</li>
<li data-start="439" data-end="457">
<p data-start="441" data-end="457">Mobile optimized</p>
</li>
<li data-start="458" data-end="482">
<p data-start="460" data-end="482">Clean automotive style</p>
</li>
<li data-start="483" data-end="508">
<p data-start="485" data-end="508">Easy <code data-start="490" data-end="498">/admin</code> dashboard</p>
</li>
<li data-start="509" data-end="530">
<p data-start="511" data-end="530">SEO basics built in</p>
</li>
<li data-start="531" data-end="545">
<p data-start="533" data-end="545">Fast loading</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="547" data-end="550">
<p data-start="552" data-end="632">Before I generate the full downloadable package, I need 3 quick things from you:</p>
<h3 data-start="634" data-end="648">1️⃣ Logo</h3>
<p data-start="649" data-end="697">Upload the Bev’s Repair logo file you want used.</p>
<h3 data-start="699" data-end="716">2️⃣ Reviews</h3>
<p data-start="717" data-end="729">Do you want:</p>
<ul data-start="730" data-end="810">
<li data-start="730" data-end="763">
<p data-start="732" data-end="763">Google reviews pulled manually?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="764" data-end="810">
<p data-start="766" data-end="810">Or I add 3 placeholder testimonials for now?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="812" data-end="829">3️⃣ Gallery</h3>
<p data-start="830" data-end="842">Do you want:</p>
<ul data-start="843" data-end="934">
<li data-start="843" data-end="885">
<p data-start="845" data-end="885">I add placeholder repair images for now?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="886" data-end="934">
<p data-start="888" data-end="934">Or leave gallery blank so you upload your own?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="936" data-end="939">
<p data-start="941" data-end="967">As soon as you reply with:</p>
<ul data-start="968" data-end="1008">
<li data-start="968" data-end="974">
<p data-start="970" data-end="974">Logo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="975" data-end="991">
<p data-start="977" data-end="991">Reviews choice</p>
</li>
<li data-start="992" data-end="1008">
<p data-start="994" data-end="1008">Gallery choice</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1024">I’ll generate:</p>
<ul data-start="1025" data-end="1167">
<li data-start="1025" data-end="1065">
