I’ll walk you through the <strong data-start="71" data-end="88">simplest path</strong> to get your site live with <strong data-start="116" data-end="136">$0/month hosting</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="139" data-end="222">We’ll use <strong data-start="149" data-end="169">GitHub + Netlify</strong>. It sounds technical but it’s actually pretty quick.</p>
<hr data-start="224" data-end="227">
<h1 data-start="229" data-end="263">Step 1 — Create a GitHub account</h1>
<p data-start="264" data-end="270">Go to:</p>
<p data-start="272" data-end="293">👉 <a data-start="275" data-end="293" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/">https://github.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="295" data-end="335">Create an account if you don’t have one.</p>
<hr data-start="337" data-end="340">
<h1 data-start="342" data-end="372">Step 2 — Create a repository</h1>
<p data-start="373" data-end="388">Once logged in:</p>
<ol data-start="390" data-end="429">
<li data-start="390" data-end="417">
<p data-start="393" data-end="417">Click <strong data-start="399" data-end="417">New repository</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="418" data-end="429">
<p data-start="421" data-end="429">Name it:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="431" data-end="454"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>bevsrepair-site</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="3" data-start="456" data-end="519">
<li data-start="456" data-end="488">
<p data-start="459" data-end="488">Leave everything else default</p>
</li>
<li data-start="489" data-end="519">
<p data-start="492" data-end="519">Click <strong data-start="498" data-end="519">Create repository</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="521" data-end="524">
<h1 data-start="526" data-end="562">Step 3 — Upload your website files</h1>
<p data-start="563" data-end="586">On the repository page:</p>
<ol data-start="588" data-end="692">
<li data-start="588" data-end="613">
