<p data-start="69" data-end="215">The records you see (sparkpost, domainkey, autodiscover) are <strong data-start="130" data-end="147">email-related</strong> and you <strong data-start="156" data-end="183">should leave them alone</strong>. They won’t affect the website.</p>
<p data-start="217" data-end="302">You just need to <strong data-start="234" data-end="255">add 3 new records</strong> for <strong data-start="260" data-end="301"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="304" data-end="307">
<h1 data-start="309" data-end="353">What to ADD (do not delete the ones shown)</h1>
<p data-start="355" data-end="390">Scroll to the bottom and add these:</p>
<h3 data-start="392" data-end="404">Record 1</h3>
<p data-start="405" data-end="417">Type<br data-start="409" data-end="412">
