<p data-start="52" data-end="143"><strong data-start="52" data-end="66">Good news:</strong><br data-start="66" data-end="69">
You <strong data-start="73" data-end="143">do NOT need to delete any of the records shown in this screenshot.</strong></p>
<p data-start="145" data-end="252">Everything visible here is <strong data-start="172" data-end="195">email configuration</strong> from <strong data-start="201" data-end="242"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Webador</span></span></strong>, such as:</p>
<ul data-start="254" data-end="389">
<li data-start="254" data-end="278">
<p data-start="256" data-end="278"><code data-start="256" data-end="278">sparkpost._domainkey</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="279" data-end="301">
<p data-start="281" data-end="301"><code data-start="281" data-end="301">jouwweb._domainkey</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="302" data-end="325">
<p data-start="304" data-end="325"><code data-start="304" data-end="325">mandrill._domainkey</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="326" data-end="342">
<p data-start="328" data-end="342"><code data-start="328" data-end="342">autodiscover</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="343" data-end="365">
<p data-start="345" data-end="365"><code data-start="345" data-end="365">_autodiscover._tcp</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="366" data-end="374">
<p data-start="368" data-end="374"><code data-start="368" data-end="374">mail</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="375" data-end="389">
<p data-start="377" data-end="389"><code data-start="377" data-end="389">autoconfig</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="391" data-end="456">Those should <strong data-start="404" data-end="432">stay exactly as they are</strong> so email keeps working.</p>
<hr data-start="458" data-end="461">
<h3 data-start="463" data-end="490">What we are looking for</h3>
<p data-start="491" data-end="550">The record that needs removing will look like one of these:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="552" data-end="604"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Type: A</span><br><span>Name: @</span><br><span>Value: something.webador.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="606" data-end="608">or</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="610" data-end="654"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Type: A</span><br><span>Name: @</span><br><span>Value: an IP address</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="656" data-end="658">or</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="660" data-end="706"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Type: CNAME</span><br><span>Name: @</span><br><span>Value: webador.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="708" data-end="776">That record controls where <strong data-start="735" data-end="752">bevsrepair.ca</strong> points for the website.</p>
<hr data-start="778" data-end="781">
<h3 data-start="783" data-end="802">What to do next</h3>
<p data-start="803" data-end="875">Scroll <strong data-start="810" data-end="839">further down the DNS page</strong> and send the <strong data-start="853" data-end="874">second screenshot</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="877" data-end="964">The record we want to remove will almost always be <strong data-start="928" data-end="947">near the bottom</strong> of the DNS list.</p>
<p data-start="966" data-end="1112">Once we remove that one, you will be able to add the <strong data-start="1019" data-end="1038">Netlify records</strong> and the domain will connect to <strong data-start="1070" data-end="1111"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></strong>.</p>
