<p data-start="155" data-end="283">That <strong data-start="160" data-end="184">wildcard CNAME (<code data-start="178" data-end="181">*</code>)</strong> forces <strong data-start="192" data-end="207">all traffic</strong> to Webador.<br data-start="219" data-end="222">
Because of that, Webador won’t allow the new Netlify records.</p>
<hr data-start="285" data-end="288">
