<p data-start="126" data-end="201">From your screenshots I can see <strong data-start="158" data-end="187">two records that conflict</strong> with Netlify.</p>
<p data-start="203" data-end="240">You need to delete <strong data-start="222" data-end="239">both of these</strong>:</p>
