<blockquote data-start="1890" data-end="2110">
<p data-start="1892" data-end="2110">Bev’s Repair Inc. has been serving Manitou and the surrounding area since 1979. Our team specializes in collision repair, refinishing, and mechanical service with a focus on quality workmanship and clear communication.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2112" data-end="2115">
