<p data-start="2144" data-end="2171">Important for local search.</p>
<p data-start="2173" data-end="2233"><strong data-start="2173" data-end="2194">Bev’s Repair Inc.</strong><br data-start="2194" data-end="2197">
13025 Rd 48W<br data-start="2209" data-end="2212">
Manitou, MB R0G 1G0</p>
<p data-start="2235" data-end="2278">📞 204-242-2318<br data-start="2250" data-end="2253">
📧 <a data-start="2256" data-end="2276" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer" rel="noopener">bevsrepair@gmail.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
