<h1 data-start="2316" data-end="2359">⭐ Optional Features (Very Good for Shops)</h1>
<p data-start="2361" data-end="2390">These improve the site a lot:</p>
<h3 data-start="2392" data-end="2416">Online Estimate Form</h3>
<p data-start="2417" data-end="2448">Customers upload damage photos.</p>
<h3 data-start="2450" data-end="2474">Insurance Claim Info</h3>
<p data-start="2475" data-end="2501">Helpful for MPI customers.</p>
<h3 data-start="2503" data-end="2526">Repair Process Page</h3>
<p data-start="2527" data-end="2536">Explains:</p>
