 h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Entry #123 by Arman78080 for Collision Repair Shop Website Design ..."><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://cdn2.f-cdn.com/contestentries/2527871/82048357/67beeb190c0e8_thumb900.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./shop-hero_files/OIP.Yog5yVPxySZyvPiAYuEdwgHacS" style="opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div><div class="border-token-border-default relative aspect-square w-32 shrink-0 rounded-xl border-[0.5px] md:shrink max-h-48 sm:w-[calc((100%-0.5rem)/4)] rounded-e-xl"><div class="group/search-image @container/search-image relative rounded-[inherit] h-full w-full" style="aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;"><button type="button" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]" aria-label="Open image details for Indianapolis Web Design Projects | Indy Web Design"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><img alt="https://www.webdesignindy.com/portfolio/uploads/collision-repair-website-design.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" class="bg-token-main-surface-tertiary m-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="./shop-hero_files/OIP.6fBTQDpuC7BrrfAy_tX3VAHaFj" style="opacity: 1;"></div></button></div></div></div>
<p data-start="42" data-end="136">Yes — and yep, I can add an <strong data-start="70" data-end="94">online estimate tool</strong> (with photo upload) right into your site.</p>
<h2 data-start="138" data-end="207">Design concept for Bev’s Repair (gold/black, professional, simple)</h2>
<p data-start="208" data-end="270">This is the layout I’d recommend (matches the examples above):</p>
<ul data-start="272" data-end="614">
<li data-start="272" data-end="370">
<p data-start="274" data-end="370"><strong data-start="274" data-end="287">Top hero:</strong> “Collision • Mechanical • Glass” + big <strong data-start="327" data-end="339">Call Now</strong> + <strong data-start="342" data-end="362">Request Estimate</strong> buttons</p>
</li>
<li data-start="371" data-end="438">
<p data-start="373" data-end="438"><strong data-start="373" data-end="393">4 service cards:</strong> Collision, Paint/Refinish, Mechanical, Glass</p>
</li>
<li data-start="439" data-end="492">
<p data-start="441" data-end="492"><strong data-start="441" data-end="464">Before/After strip:</strong> 3–6 jobs (super high trust)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="493" data-end="549">
<p data-start="495" data-end="549"><strong data-start="495" data-end="515">Reviews preview:</strong> 3 short Google reviews with stars</p>
</li>
<li data-start="550" data-end="614">
<p data-start="552" data-end="614"><strong data-start="552" data-end="579">Location + hours + map:</strong> everything visible without hunting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="616" data-end="732">If you like, we can make your homepage look <em data-start="660" data-end="686">more like those examples</em> while still keeping it fast + easy to manage.</p>
<h2 data-start="734" data-end="772">Online estimate tool (what I added)</h2>
<p data-start="773" data-end="824">I updated your Contact/Quote form so customers can:</p>
<ul data-start="825" data-end="917">
<li data-start="825" data-end="855">
<p data-start="827" data-end="855">enter vehicle + claim number</p>
</li>
<li data-start="856" data-end="889">
<p data-start="858" data-end="889">choose preferred contact method</p>
</li>
<li data-start="890" data-end="917">
<p data-start="892" data-end="917"><strong data-start="892" data-end="917">upload up to 3 photos</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="919" data-end="1120">Important: Netlify forms supports file uploads, but the request size limit is around <strong data-start="1004" data-end="1012">8 MB</strong>, and it’s <strong data-start="1023" data-end="1045">one file per field</strong> (so we use 3 separate photo fields). <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 65px;"><a href="https://docs.netlify.com/manage/forms/setup/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://docs.netlify.com/manage/forms/setup/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" style="max-width: 65px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Netlify Docs</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h3 data-start="1122" data-end="1186">Download the updated site ZIP (with estimate + photo upload)</h3>
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1294"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">Download bevsrepair_site_v2_estimate_upload.zip</button></span></p>
<h2 data-start="1296" data-end="1339">What you do next (after DNS goes active)</h2>
<ol data-start="1340" data-end="1616">
<li data-start="1340" data-end="1442">
<p data-start="1343" data-end="1442"><strong data-start="1343" data-end="1377">Replace your GitHub repo files</strong> with the contents of this new ZIP (or upload/commit over top).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1443" data-end="1471">
<p data-start="1446" data-end="1471">Netlify will auto-deploy.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1472" data-end="1616">
<p data-start="1475" data-end="1498">Test the estimate form:</p>
<ul data-start="1502" data-end="1616">
<li data-start="1502" data-end="1521">
<p data-start="1504" data-end="1521">Go to <strong data-start="1510" data-end="1521">Contact</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1525" data-end="1550">
<p data-start="1527" data-end="1550">Upload 1–2 small photos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1554" data-end="1562">
<p data-start="1556" data-end="1562">Submit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1566" data-end="1616">
<p data-start="1568" data-end="1616">Check Netlify → <strong data-start="1584" data-end="1593">Forms</strong> tab for the submission</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1618" data-end="1790">If you want, tell me what you’d like the estimate form to ask (ex: “drivable?”, “preferred drop-off date?”, “MPI claim started?”) and I’ll tailor it to your exact workflow.</p>

