<p data-start="80" data-end="151">Now let’s make sure everything is <strong data-start="114" data-end="150">fully live and working correctly</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="153" data-end="156">
<h1 data-start="158" data-end="181">1️⃣ Check the website</h1>
<p data-start="182" data-end="209">Open these in your browser:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="211" data-end="240"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://bevsrepair.ca</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="242" data-end="245">and</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="247" data-end="280"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://www.bevsrepair.ca</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="282" data-end="362">You should see the <strong data-start="301" data-end="361">new site hosted on <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></strong>.</p>
<p data-start="364" data-end="475">If you still see the old site, it just means <strong data-start="409" data-end="449">DNS hasn’t propagated everywhere yet</strong> (can take up to ~1 hour).</p>
<hr data-start="477" data-end="480">
<h1 data-start="482" data-end="506">2️⃣ Check SSL security</h1>
<p data-start="507" data-end="531">Look at the address bar.</p>
<p data-start="533" data-end="549">You want to see:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="551" data-end="583"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>🔒 https://bevsrepair.ca</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="585" data-end="592">If not:</p>
<p data-start="594" data-end="611">In Netlify go to:</p>
<p data-start="613" data-end="658"><strong data-start="613" data-end="658">Site Settings → Domain Management → HTTPS</strong></p>
<p data-start="660" data-end="666">Click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="668" data-end="697"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Provision certificate</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="699" data-end="757">Netlify will install a free SSL certificate automatically.</p>
<hr data-start="759" data-end="762">
<h1 data-start="764" data-end="792">3️⃣ Test the estimate form</h1>
<p data-start="793" data-end="798">Open:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="800" data-end="829"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>bevsrepair.ca/contact</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="831" data-end="840">Fill out:</p>
<ul data-start="842" data-end="888">
<li data-start="842" data-end="848">
<p data-start="844" data-end="848">Name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="849" data-end="856">
<p data-start="851" data-end="856">Phone</p>
</li>
<li data-start="857" data-end="866">
<p data-start="859" data-end="866">Vehicle</p>
</li>
<li data-start="867" data-end="888">
<p data-start="869" data-end="888">Upload a test photo</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="890" data-end="900">Submit it.</p>
<p data-start="902" data-end="924">Then check in Netlify:</p>
<p data-start="926" data-end="949"><strong data-start="926" data-end="949">Forms → Submissions</strong></p>
<p data-start="951" data-end="993">You should see the estimate request there.</p>
<hr data-start="995" data-end="998">
<h1 data-start="1000" data-end="1028">4️⃣ Install your real logo</h1>
<p data-start="1029" data-end="1073">Right now the site still uses a placeholder.</p>
<p data-start="1075" data-end="1117">Replace it with the logo you sent earlier.</p>
<p data-start="1119" data-end="1135">Put the file in:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1137" data-end="1156"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/img/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1158" data-end="1173">Then rename it:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1175" data-end="1191"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>logo.png</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1193" data-end="1237">That will make it appear in the site header.</p>
<hr data-start="1239" data-end="1242">
<h1 data-start="1244" data-end="1273">5️⃣ Add real gallery photos</h1>
<p data-start="1274" data-end="1310">Replace the placeholder images with:</p>
<ul data-start="1312" data-end="1391">
<li data-start="1312" data-end="1344">
<p data-start="1314" data-end="1344">before/after collision repairs</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1345" data-end="1357">
<p data-start="1347" data-end="1357">paint work</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1358" data-end="1371">
<p data-start="1360" data-end="1371">shop photos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1372" data-end="1391">
<p data-start="1374" data-end="1391">finished vehicles</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1393" data-end="1405">These go in:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1407" data-end="1426"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/img/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1428" data-end="1472">Then update them in the <strong data-start="1452" data-end="1471">Gallery section</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1474" data-end="1477">
<h1 data-start="1479" data-end="1508">6️⃣ Enable the admin editor</h1>
<p data-start="1509" data-end="1552">This lets you update the site easily later.</p>
<p data-start="1554" data-end="1560">Go to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1562" data-end="1589"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>bevsrepair.ca/admin</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1591" data-end="1607">Then in Netlify:</p>
<ol data-start="1609" data-end="1682">
<li data-start="1609" data-end="1633">
<p data-start="1612" data-end="1633"><strong data-start="1612" data-end="1633">Identity → Enable</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1634" data-end="1661">
<p data-start="1637" data-end="1661"><strong data-start="1637" data-end="1661">Git Gateway → Enable</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1662" data-end="1682">
<p data-start="1665" data-end="1682">Invite your email</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1684" data-end="1701">Now you can edit:</p>
<ul data-start="1703" data-end="1740">
<li data-start="1703" data-end="1713">
<p data-start="1705" data-end="1713">services</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1714" data-end="1723">
<p data-start="1716" data-end="1723">reviews</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1724" data-end="1733">
<p data-start="1726" data-end="1733">gallery</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1734" data-end="1740">
<p data-start="1736" data-end="1740">text</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1742" data-end="1764">without touching code.</p>
<hr data-start="1766" data-end="1769">
<h1 data-start="1771" data-end="1808">7️⃣ Cancel the Webador website plan</h1>
<p data-start="1809" data-end="1918">Once everything works, you can cancel the <strong data-start="1851" data-end="1872">site builder plan</strong> in <strong data-start="1876" data-end="1917"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Webador</span></span></strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1920" data-end="1958">Just keep the <strong data-start="1934" data-end="1957">domain registration</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1960" data-end="1963">
<h1 data-start="1965" data-end="1994">🚀 Next upgrade I recommend</h1>
<p data-start="1995" data-end="2051">Now that your site is live, I’d strongly suggest we add:</p>
<ul data-start="2053" data-end="2236">
<li data-start="2053" data-end="2096">
<p data-start="2055" data-end="2096"><strong data-start="2055" data-end="2096">Google review stars in search results</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2097" data-end="2132">
<p data-start="2099" data-end="2132"><strong data-start="2099" data-end="2132">Before / After slider gallery</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2133" data-end="2172">
<p data-start="2135" data-end="2172"><strong data-start="2135" data-end="2172">Online estimate with photo upload</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2173" data-end="2208">
<p data-start="2175" data-end="2208"><strong data-start="2175" data-end="2208">SEO for “autobody Manitou MB”</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2209" data-end="2236">
<p data-start="2211" data-end="2236"><strong data-start="2211" data-end="2236">Mobile quick-call bar</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2238" data-end="2337">Those things make a <strong data-start="2258" data-end="2308">small shop website look extremely professional</strong> and help bring in more work.</p>
<hr data-start="2339" data-end="2342">
<p data-start="2344" data-end="2470" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, I can also show you <strong data-start="2377" data-end="2469">one big upgrade that would make your site look 10× more professional in about 10 minutes</strong>.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class