ly"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="bbb21349-12e4-4be5-8195-30aa9df54465" data-testid="conversation-turn-65" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h5 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="bbb21349-12e4-4be5-8195-30aa9df54465" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">It still isnt working </div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="f214295a-0f9b-40aa-b17d-1681bf1750f8" data-testid="conversation-turn-66" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="f214295a-0f9b-40aa-b17d-1681bf1750f8" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="161">You're <strong data-start="7" data-end="21">very close</strong> — the good news is your screenshot proves the site is <strong data-start="76" data-end="138">already loading from <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></strong>, so DNS is correct. 👍</p>
<p data-start="163" data-end="257">The reason HTTPS still fails is simply that <strong data-start="207" data-end="256">Netlify hasn't issued the SSL certificate yet</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="259" data-end="333">This happens when Netlify's DNS check ran <strong data-start="301" data-end="332">before propagation finished</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="335" data-end="338">
<h1 data-start="340" data-end="368">Fix it in about 30 seconds</h1>
<p data-start="370" data-end="420">Go back to the page you showed earlier in Netlify.</p>
<p data-start="422" data-end="440">Click this button:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="442" data-end="472"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Retry DNS verification</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="474" data-end="503">Wait about <strong data-start="485" data-end="502">10–20 seconds</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="505" data-end="572">If it works, the message will change and you’ll see something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="574" data-end="603"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Provision certificate</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="605" data-end="619">Then click it.</p>
<hr data-start="621" data-end="624">
<h1 data-start="626" data-end="638">After that</h1>
<p data-start="639" data-end="701">Netlify will install a <strong data-start="662" data-end="700">free Let's Encrypt SSL certificate</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="703" data-end="736">It usually takes <strong data-start="720" data-end="735">1–2 minutes</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="738" data-end="750">Then enable:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="752" data-end="771"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Force HTTPS</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="773" data-end="795">Your site will become:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="797" data-end="826"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://bevsrepair.ca</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="828" data-end="845">with the 🔒 lock.</p>
<hr data-start="847" data-end="850">
<h1 data-start="852" data-end="879">If the button still fails</h1>
<p data-start="880" data-end="928">Sometimes Netlify caches the DNS check. Do this:</p>
<p data-start="930" data-end="1036">1️⃣ Click <strong data-start="940" data-end="966">Retry DNS verification</strong><br data-start="966" data-end="969">
2️⃣ Wait <strong data-start="978" data-end="992">60 seconds</strong><br data-start="992" data-end="995">
3️⃣ Refresh the page<br data-start="1015" data-end="1018">
4️⃣ Click it again</p>
<p data-start="1038" data-end="1060">That usually fixes it.</p>
<hr data-start="1062" data-end="1065">
<h1 data-start="1067" data-end="1086">Quick test for me</h1>
<p data-start="1087" data-end="1139">Before we go further, try opening this in a browser:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1141" data-end="1173"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>http://www.bevsrepair.ca</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1175" data-end="1205">Tell me if it loads your site.</p>
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1319" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">This tells me whether the <strong data-start="1233" data-end="1259">CNAME record for <code data-start="1252" data-end="1257">www</code></strong> has propagated yet, which affects the certificate issuance.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#2126ae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Share" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" id="radix-_r_3f8_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="cursor-pointer touch:px-2.5 text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary h-[30px] rounded-md px-1.5" aria-label="Switch model"><div class="flex items-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ec66f0" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="More actions" type="button" id="radix-_r_c8_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="bbb21a32-67e2-411c-ae46-9f857865baa2" data-testid="conversation-turn-67" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h5 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="bbb21a32-67e2-411c-ae46-9f857865baa2" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Nope still not working</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="c47663a1-5355-43dc-930b-5a6b0c74b8ca" data-testid="conversation-turn-68" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div class="absolute flex h-8 w-3 origin-center items-center justify-center" style="opacity: 0; transform: scale(0);"><div class="bg-token-text-primary h-3 w-3 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="relative my-1 min-h-6"><div class="relative flex origin-top-left flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-clip rtl:origin-top-right" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="relative w-full text-start"><div class="flex w-full flex-row items-start justify-between gap-4 text-start"><button class="flex min-w-0 shrink-1 gap-0.5 items-center"><span class="font-medium w-full"><span class="flex gap-1 text-start align-middle items-center truncate text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary dark:text-[var(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)]" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="flex min-w-0 gap-1 items-center"><span class="min-w-0 truncate">Thought for 13s</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></span></button></div></div><div class="max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))]"></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="762e52e0-b564-4aa1-a5f6-645b0a40c2f4" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="98">Got it — when you say “still not working,” based on what we’ve seen so far it almost always means:</p>
<ul data-start="100" data-end="244">
<li data-start="100" data-end="151">
<p data-start="102" data-end="151"><strong data-start="102" data-end="128">the site loads on http</strong> (you showed that), but</p>
</li>
<li data-start="152" data-end="244">
<p data-start="154" data-end="244"><strong data-start="154" data-end="178">HTTPS won’t activate</strong> because <strong data-start="187" data-end="230">Netlify still can’t verify BOTH domains</strong> (root + www).</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="246" data-end="297">Netlify won’t issue the certificate until <strong data-start="288" data-end="296">both</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="298" data-end="372">
<li data-start="298" data-end="315">
<p data-start="300" data-end="315"><code data-start="300" data-end="315">bevsrepair.ca</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="316" data-end="372">
<p data-start="318" data-end="372"><code data-start="318" data-end="337">www.bevsrepair.ca</code><br>
are pointing at Netlify correctly.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="374" data-end="407">Here’s the fastest way to fix it.</p>
<hr data-start="409" data-end="412">
<h2 data-start="414" data-end="472">1) Fix the “www” side first (this is the usual culprit)</h2>
<p data-start="474" data-end="545">Go back to <strong data-start="485" data-end="509">Webador → Modify DNS</strong> and make sure you have this record:</p>
<p data-start="547" data-end="556"><strong data-start="547" data-end="556">CNAME</strong></p>
<ul data-start="557" data-end="697">
<li data-start="557" data-end="574">
<p data-start="559" data-end="574"><strong data-start="559" data-end="568">Name:</strong> <code data-start="569" data-end="574">www</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="575" data-end="660">
<p data-start="577" data-end="660"><strong data-start="577" data-end="587">Value:</strong> <code data-start="588" data-end="627">sprightly-monstera-5d76d8.netlify.app</code>  ✅ (must include <code data-start="645" data-end="659">.netlify.app</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="661" data-end="697">
<p data-start="663" data-end="697">(NO <code data-start="667" data-end="676">http://</code> and no extra spaces)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="699" data-end="855">If you accidentally put the CNAME under a blank name, or typed <code data-start="762" data-end="789">sprightly-monstera-5d76d8</code> without the <code data-start="802" data-end="816">.netlify.app</code>, <code data-start="818" data-end="823">www</code> won’t work and HTTPS will fail.</p>
<p data-start="857" data-end="960">Also confirm there is <strong data-start="879" data-end="908">NO other record for <code data-start="901" data-end="906">www</code></strong> (no A record for <code data-start="926" data-end="931">www</code>, no second CNAME for <code data-start="953" data-end="958">www</code>).</p>
<hr data-start="962" data-end="965">
<h2 data-start="967" data-end="1013">2) Confirm the root domain (“@”) is correct</h2>
<p data-start="1015" data-end="1080">In Webador you should have <strong data-start="1042" data-end="1059">two A records</strong> for the root domain.</p>
<p data-start="1082" data-end="1229">Depending on Webador, the “Name” might be <code data-start="1124" data-end="1127">@</code> <strong data-start="1128" data-end="1152">or it might be blank</strong> (both are common in different DNS panels). The important part is the values:</p>
<p data-start="1231" data-end="1250"><strong data-start="1231" data-end="1250">A record (root)</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1251" data-end="1294">
<li data-start="1251" data-end="1273">
<p data-start="1253" data-end="1273">Name: <code data-start="1259" data-end="1262">@</code> (or blank)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1274" data-end="1294">
<p data-start="1276" data-end="1294">Value: <code data-start="1283" data-end="1294">75.2.60.5</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1296" data-end="1315"><strong data-start="1296" data-end="1315">A record (root)</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1316" data-end="1363">
<li data-start="1316" data-end="1338">
<p data-start="1318" data-end="1338">Name: <code data-start="1324" data-end="1327">@</code> (or blank)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1339" data-end="1363">
<p data-start="1341" data-end="1363">Value: <code data-start="1348" data-end="1363">99.83.190.102</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1365" data-end="1423">And make sure you deleted the old Webador website records:</p>
<ul data-start="1424" data-end="1525">
<li data-start="1424" data-end="1466">
<p data-start="1426" data-end="1466"><strong data-start="1426" data-end="1431">A</strong> with value <code data-start="1443" data-end="1457">35.204.150.5</code> ✅ delete</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1467" data-end="1525">
<p data-start="1469" data-end="1525"><strong data-start="1469" data-end="1478">CNAME</strong> <code data-start="1479" data-end="1482">*</code> → <code data-start="1485" data-end="1516">website-rendering.webador.com</code> ✅ delete</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1527" data-end="1530">
<h2 data-start="1532" data-end="1585">3) Make Netlify re-check and issue the certificate</h2>
<p data-start="1587" data-end="1598">In Netlify:</p>
<ol data-start="1599" data-end="1889">
<li data-start="1599" data-end="1644">
<p data-start="1602" data-end="1644"><strong data-start="1602" data-end="1644">Site configuration → Domain management</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1645" data-end="1728">
<p data-start="1648" data-end="1682">Make sure both domains are listed:</p>
<ul data-start="1686" data-end="1728">
<li data-start="1686" data-end="1703">
<p data-start="1688" data-end="1703"><code data-start="1688" data-end="1703">bevsrepair.ca</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1707" data-end="1728">
<p data-start="1709" data-end="1728"><code data-start="1709" data-end="1728">www.bevsrepair.ca</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1729" data-end="1752">
<p data-start="1732" data-end="1752">Then go to <strong data-start="1743" data-end="1752">HTTPS</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1753" data-end="1788">
<p data-start="1756" data-end="1788">Click <strong data-start="1762" data-end="1788">Retry DNS verification</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1789" data-end="1842">
<p data-start="1792" data-end="1842">When it allows it, click <strong data-start="1817" data-end="1842">Provision certificate</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1843" data-end="1889">
<p data-start="1846" data-end="1889">After it provisions, enable <strong data-start="1874" data-end="1889">Force HTTPS</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1891" data-end="1894">
<h2 data-start="1896" data-end="1934">4) Quick “is www working yet?” test</h2>
<p data-start="1935" data-end="1947">Try opening:</p>
<ul data-start="1949" data-end="1977">
<li data-start="1949" data-end="1977">
<p data-start="1951" data-end="1977"><code data-start="1951" data-end="1977">http://www.bevsrepair.ca</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1979" data-end="2089">If that does <strong data-start="1992" data-end="1999">not</strong> load your site, HTTPS will not provision yet — and the fix is the <strong data-start="2066" data-end="2075">CNAME</strong> record above.</p>
<hr data-start="2091" data-end="2094">
<h2 data-start="2096" data-end="2131">If you want the fastest pinpoint</h2>
<p data-start="2132" data-end="2189">Tell me what happens when you open <strong data-start="2167" data-end="2178">exactly</strong> these two:</p>
<ol data-start="2191" data-end="2248">
<li data-start="2191" data-end="2218">
<p data-start="2194" data-end="2218"><code data-start="2194" data-end="2216">http://bevsrepair.ca</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2219" data-end="2248">
<p data-start="2222" data-end="2248"><code data-start="2222" data-end="2248">http://www.bevsrepair.ca</code></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="2250" data-end="2414" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Or snap a photo of your Webador DNS list showing the <strong data-start="2303" data-end="2320">two A records</strong> and the <strong data-start="2329" data-end="2342">www CNAME</strong> (just that section). I’ll tell you exactly what’s wrong in one message.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-co