<p data-start="66" data-end="88">Your screenshots show:</p>
<ul data-start="90" data-end="276">
<li data-start="90" data-end="136">
<p data-start="92" data-end="136"><code data-start="92" data-end="107">bevsrepair.ca</code> is already loading your site</p>
</li>
<li data-start="137" data-end="207">
<p data-start="139" data-end="207">DNS records in <strong data-start="154" data-end="195"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Webador</span></span></strong> are correct</p>
</li>
<li data-start="208" data-end="233">
<p data-start="210" data-end="233">Netlify sees the domain</p>
</li>
<li data-start="234" data-end="276">
<p data-start="236" data-end="276">Only the <strong data-start="245" data-end="265">SSL verification</strong> is failing</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="278" data-end="350">That almost always means <strong data-start="303" data-end="349">global DNS propagation hasn’t finished yet</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="352" data-end="490">Even though <strong data-start="364" data-end="401">your computer can see the new DNS</strong>, Netlify checks DNS from many locations around the world before issuing the certificate.</p>
<p data-start="492" data-end="507">Typical timing:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="509" data-end="591"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>DNS propagation: 30 minutes – 2 hours</span><br><span>SSL issuance after that: 1–5 minutes</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="593" data-end="651">Sometimes it can take <strong data-start="615" data-end="633">up to 24 hours</strong>, but usually not.</p>
<hr data-start="653" data-end="656">
<h2 data-start="658" data-end="683">What you should do now</h2>
<p data-start="684" data-end="735">Just leave everything as it is and try again later.</p>
<p data-start="737" data-end="757">In about <strong data-start="746" data-end="756">1 hour</strong>:</p>
<ol data-start="759" data-end="856">
<li data-start="759" data-end="809">
<p data-start="762" data-end="809">Go to <strong data-start="768" data-end="809"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="810" data-end="847">
<p data-start="813" data-end="847">Open <strong data-start="818" data-end="847">Domain management → HTTPS</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="848" data-end="856">
<p data-start="851" data-end="856">Click</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="858" data-end="888"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Retry DNS verification</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="890" data-end="909">Then you should see</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="911" data-end="940"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Provision certificate</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="942" data-end="961">After that, enable:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="963" data-end="982"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Force HTTPS</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="984" data-end="987">
<h2 data-start="989" data-end="1018">Good sign you already have</h2>
<p data-start="1019" data-end="1066">Your browser already shows the site loading at:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1068" data-end="1089"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>bevsrepair.ca</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1091" data-end="1128">That means the <strong data-start="1106" data-end="1127">hard part is done</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1130" data-end="1206">This last step is just the certificate waiting for DNS to settle everywhere.</p>
<hr data-start="1208" data-end="1211">
<h2 data-start="1213" data-end="1229">While we wait</h2>
<p data-start="1230" data-end="1373">Once HTTPS works, I’d like to help you make <strong data-start="1274" data-end="1302">three quick improvements</strong> that will make the site look <strong data-start="1332" data-end="1372">much more professional for customers</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="1375" data-end="1489">
<li data-start="1375" data-end="1410">
<p data-start="1377" data-end="1410">Larger <strong data-start="1384" data-end="1410">Bev’s Repair gold logo</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1411" data-end="1444">
<p data-start="1413" data-end="1444"><strong data-start="1413" data-end="1444">Before/after repair gallery</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1445" data-end="1489">
<p data-start="1447" data-end="1489"><strong data-start="1447" data-end="1489">Online estimate form with photo upload</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1491" data-end="1568" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Those take about <strong data-start="1508" data-end="1522">10 minutes</strong> and make a big difference for a shop website.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#2126ae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Share" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" id="radix-_r_3fq_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="cursor-pointer touch:px-2.5 text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary h-[30px] rounded-md px-1.5" aria-label="Switch model"><div class="flex items-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ec66f0" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="More actions" type="button" id="radix-_r_e0_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="bbb218a1-e7a8-4cdf-a2bd-3d61050a2efb" data-testid="conversation-turn-81" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h5 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="bbb218a1-e7a8-4cdf-a2bd-3d61050a2efb" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Is there anything I can do while we wait? </div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="e7f8bdda-dd6a-46cc-8658-39bdf718f6c6" data-testid="conversation-turn-82" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e7f8bdda-dd6a-46cc-8658-39bdf718f6c6" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="215">Yes — actually there are <strong data-start="25" data-end="76">a few really useful things you can do right now</strong> while the SSL finishes propagating. None of these will interfere with the DNS, and they’ll make the site much better once HTTPS activates.</p>
<hr data-start="217" data-end="220">
<h1 data-start="222" data-end="253">1️⃣ Add your real shop photos</h1>
<p data-start="254" data-end="297">Right now your site has placeholder images.</p>
<p data-start="299" data-end="318">Good photos to add:</p>
<ul data-start="320" data-end="416">
<li data-start="320" data-end="335">
<p data-start="322" data-end="335">shop exterior</p>
</li>
<li data-start="336" data-end="349">
<p data-start="338" data-end="349">paint booth</p>
</li>
<li data-start="350" data-end="363">
<p data-start="352" data-end="363">repair work</p>
</li>
<li data-start="364" data-end="396">
<p data-start="366" data-end="396">before/after collision repairs</p>
</li>
<li data-start="397" data-end="416">
<p data-start="399" data-end="416">finished vehicles</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="418" data-end="479">These go in the <strong data-start="434" data-end="453">gallery section</strong> and build a lot of trust.</p>
<p data-start="481" data-end="524">Customers love seeing <strong data-start="503" data-end="523">real repair work</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="526" data-end="529">
<h1 data-start="531" data-end="564">2️⃣ Prepare before/after photos</h1>
<p data-start="565" data-end="612">One of the best sections for autobody shops is:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="614" data-end="643"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Before → After repair</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="645" data-end="660">Example layout:</p>
<ul data-start="662" data-end="754">
<li data-start="662" data-end="686">
<p data-start="664" data-end="686">dented door → repaired</p>
</li>
<li data-start="687" data-end="721">
<p data-start="689" data-end="721">front bumper damage → refinished</p>
</li>
<li data-start="722" data-end="754">
<p data-start="724" data-end="754">quarter panel repair → painted</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="756" data-end="824">Even <strong data-start="761" data-end="780">3 or 4 examples</strong> makes the site look much more professional.</p>
<hr data-start="826" data-end="829">
<h1 data-start="831" data-end="867">3️⃣ Write a short “About the shop”</h1>
<p data-start="868" data-end="900">You can add something like this:</p>
<p data-start="902" data-end="910">Example:</p>
<blockquote data-start="912" data-end="1227">
<p data-start="914" data-end="1227">Bev’s Repair Inc. has proudly served Manitou and the surrounding area since 1979. Our experienced team specializes in collision repair, mechanical service, paint refinishing, and automotive glass replacement. We focus on quality workmanship, clear communication, and getting our customers safely back on the road.</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1229" data-end="1251">Short and trustworthy.</p>
<hr data-start="1253" data-end="1256">
<h1 data-start="1258" data-end="1298">4️⃣ Prepare info for the estimate form</h1>
<p data-start="1299" data-end="1355">The online estimate tool will ask customers things like:</p>
<ul data-start="1357" data-end="1477">
<li data-start="1357" data-end="1363">
<p data-start="1359" data-end="1363">Name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1364" data-end="1371">
<p data-start="1366" data-end="1371">Phone</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1372" data-end="1401">
<p data-start="1374" data-end="1401">Vehicle year / make / model</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1402" data-end="1425">
<p data-start="1404" data-end="1425">Description of damage</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1426" data-end="1441">
<p data-start="1428" data-end="1441">Upload photos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1442" data-end="1477">
<p data-start="1444" data-end="1477">Insurance claim number (optional)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1479" data-end="1527">Think about whether you want to add things like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1529" data-end="1612"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Is the vehicle drivable?</span><br><span>Preferred contact method?</span><br><span>Preferred drop-off date?</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1614" data-end="1617">
<h1 data-start="1619" data-end="1656">5️⃣ Claim / optimize Google listing</h1>
<p data-start="1657" data-end="1717">If you haven’t already, make sure your shop is optimized on:</p>
<p data-start="1719" data-end="1780">👉 <strong data-start="1722" data-end="1763"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Google</span></span></strong> Business Profile</p>
<p data-start="1782" data-end="1799">Make sure it has:</p>
<ul data-start="1801" data-end="1845">
<li data-start="1801" data-end="1810">
<p data-start="1803" data-end="1810">address</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1811" data-end="1818">
<p data-start="1813" data-end="1818">phone</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1819" data-end="1826">
<p data-start="1821" data-end="1826">hours</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1827" data-end="1835">
<p data-start="1829" data-end="1835">photos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1836" data-end="1845">
<p data-start="1838" data-end="1845">reviews</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1847" data-end="1898">This helps your website show up when people search:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1900" data-end="1975"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>autobody Manitou MB</span><br><span>collision repair near me</span><br><span>auto body shop Manitou</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1977" data-end="1980">
