<p data-start="76" data-end="110">Quick recap of where you left off:</p>
<p data-start="112" data-end="251">✔ Domain connected<br data-start="130" data-end="133">
✔ Site live at <strong data-start="148" data-end="165">bevsrepair.ca</strong><br data-start="165" data-end="168">
