<p data-start="253" data-end="331">So today we can make the site <strong data-start="283" data-end="330">look more like a real autobody shop website</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="333" data-end="336">
<h1 data-start="338" data-end="372">First thing to check (2 seconds)</h1>
<p data-start="373" data-end="378">Open:</p>
