<p data-start="518" data-end="592">Best practice: don’t use inline styles everywhere — change it in CSS once.</p>
<h3 data-start="594" data-end="606">Do this:</h3>
<ol data-start="607" data-end="723">
<li data-start="607" data-end="653">
<p data-start="610" data-end="653">In GitHub open: <strong data-start="626" data-end="653"><code data-start="628" data-end="651">assets/css/styles.css</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="654" data-end="702">
<p data-start="657" data-end="702">Find <code data-start="662" data-end="674">.site-logo</code> (or search for <code data-start="690" data-end="701">site-logo</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="703" data-end="723">
<p data-start="706" data-end="723">Set it like this:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="725" data-end="781"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">site-logo</span><span>{</span><br><span>  height: </span><span class="ͼj">100</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  width: </span><span class="ͼj">auto</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="783" data-end="832">If you want it bigger, change <code data-start="813" data-end="820">100px</code> to <code data-start="824" data-end="831">120px</code>.</p>
<p data-start="834" data-end="870">✅ Commit changes → refresh the site.</p>
<hr data-start="872" data-end="875">
<h1 data-start="877" data-end="949">3) Replace the 6 gallery placeholders with real photos (10–15 minutes)</h1>
<p data-start="950" data-end="1000">You’re already in: <strong data-start="969" data-end="986"><code data-start="971" data-end="984">assets/img/</code></strong> and you have:</p>
<ul data-start="1002" data-end="1037">
<li data-start="1002" data-end="1037">
<p data-start="1004" data-end="1037"><code data-start="1004" data-end="1019">gallery-1.svg</code> … <code data-start="1022" data-end="1037">gallery-6.svg</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1039" data-end="1057">Easiest method</h3>
<p data-start="1058" data-end="1119">Upload your real photos into <strong data-start="1087" data-end="1104"><code data-start="1089" data-end="1102">assets/img/</code></strong> and name them:</p>
<ul data-start="1121" data-end="1178">
<li data-start="1121" data-end="1138">
<p data-start="1123" data-end="1138"><code data-start="1123" data-end="1138">gallery-1.jpg</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1139" data-end="1156">
<p data-start="1141" data-end="1156"><code data-start="1141" data-end="1156">gallery-2.jpg</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1157" data-end="1160">
<p data-start="1159" data-end="1160">…</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1161" data-end="1178">
<p data-start="1163" data-end="1178"><code data-start="1163" data-end="1178">gallery-6.jpg</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1180" data-end="1247">Then we’ll update the gallery page to use <code data-start="1222" data-end="1228">.jpg</code> instead of <code data-start="1240" data-end="1246">.svg</code>.</p>
<h3 data-start="1249" data-end="1276">Best photo types to use</h3>
<ul data-start="1277" data-end="1373">
<li data-start="1277" data-end="1300">
<p data-start="1279" data-end="1300">2x before/after pairs</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1301" data-end="1329">
<p data-start="1303" data-end="1329">1x paint/refinish close-up</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1330" data-end="1348">
<p data-start="1332" data-end="1348">1x shop exterior</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1349" data-end="1373">
<p data-start="1351" data-end="1373">1x “team working” shot</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1375" data-end="1378">
<h1 data-start="1380" data-end="1443">4) Add the online estimate tool with photo upload (big value)</h1>
<p data-start="1444" data-end="1546">I already prepared an updated site zip that adds the estimate form + photo upload on the Contact page.</p>
<p data-start="1548" data-end="1675">✅ Download it here:<br>
<span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">Download bevsrepair_site_v2_estimate_upload.zip</button></span></p>
<h3 data-start="1677" data-end="1714">Easiest way to apply it (no code)</h3>
<p data-start="1715" data-end="1788">If you’re OK with it, we’ll just update <strong data-start="1755" data-end="1767">one file</strong> in your GitHub repo:</p>
<ul data-start="1790" data-end="1855">
<li data-start="1790" data-end="1855">
<p data-start="1792" data-end="1855">Replace your current <code data-start="1813" data-end="1827">contact.html</code> with the one from that zip.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1857" data-end="1912">Then in Netlify you’ll see submissions under <strong data-start="1902" data-end="1911">Forms</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1914" data-end="1917">
<h2 data-start="1919" data-end="1975">Quick choice so I don’t send you down the wrong path:</h2>
<p data-start="1976" data-end="2019">Do you want to update the estimate form by…</p>
<p data-start="2021" data-end="2157"><strong data-start="2021" data-end="2027">A)</strong> “Upload a single updated file (contact.html) into GitHub” (fastest)<br data-start="2095" data-end="2098">
<strong data-start="2098" data-end="2104">B)</strong> “I’ll edit the form directly in GitHub” (still easy)</p>
<p data-start="2159" data-end="2197" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Reply with <strong data-start="2170" data-end="2180">A or B</strong> and we’ll do it.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad resp