<p data-start="70" data-end="88">Your site now has:</p>
<ul data-start="90" data-end="313">
<li data-start="90" data-end="109">
<p data-start="92" data-end="109"><strong data-start="92" data-end="109">HTTPS enabled</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="110" data-end="141">
<p data-start="112" data-end="141"><strong data-start="112" data-end="141">SSL certificate installed</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="142" data-end="202">
<p data-start="144" data-end="202">Certificate from <strong data-start="161" data-end="202"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Let's Encrypt</span></span></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="203" data-end="260">
<p data-start="205" data-end="260">Covers both <strong data-start="217" data-end="234">bevsrepair.ca</strong> and <strong data-start="239" data-end="260"><a data-start="241" data-end="258" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="http://www.bevsrepair.ca/">www.bevsrepair.ca<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="261" data-end="313">
<p data-start="263" data-end="313">Auto-renew enabled (so you never need to touch it)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="315" data-end="395">So your website is now <strong data-start="338" data-end="354">fully secure</strong> and will stay that way automatically. 🔒</p>
<p data-start="397" data-end="493">You don’t need to click <strong data-start="421" data-end="442">Renew certificate</strong> or <strong data-start="446" data-end="472">Set custom certificate</strong> — leave those alone.</p>
<hr data-start="495" data-end="498">
<h1 data-start="500" data-end="525">Next thing we should do</h1>
<p data-start="526" data-end="633">Now that the technical stuff is finished, we should focus on <strong data-start="587" data-end="632">making the website stronger for customers</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="635" data-end="687">The three biggest improvements you can do today are:</p>
<h3 data-start="689" data-end="717">1️⃣ Make the logo bigger</h3>
<p data-start="718" data-end="763">We were already editing this in <code data-start="750" data-end="762">index.html</code>.</p>
<p data-start="765" data-end="794">Just change the logo line to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="796" data-end="897"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href