<p data-start="899" data-end="923">Then <strong data-start="904" data-end="922">commit changes</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="925" data-end="928">
<h3 data-start="930" data-end="958">2️⃣ Add real shop photos</h3>
<p data-start="959" data-end="999">Your gallery currently has placeholders:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1001" data-end="1092"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>gallery-1.svg</span><br><span>gallery-2.svg</span><br><span>gallery-3.svg</span><br><span>gallery-4.svg</span><br><span>gallery-5.svg</span><br><span>gallery-6.svg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1094" data-end="1112">Replace them with:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1114" data-end="1205"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>gallery-1.jpg</span><br><span>gallery-2.jpg</span><br><span>gallery-3.jpg</span><br><span>gallery-4.jpg</span><br><span>gallery-5.jpg</span><br><span>gallery-6.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1224">Good photo ideas:</p>
<ul data-start="1226" data-end="1331">
<li data-start="1226" data-end="1260">
<p data-start="1228" data-end="1260">before / after collision repairs</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1261" data-end="1274">
<p data-start="1263" data-end="1274">paint booth</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1275" data-end="1295">
<p data-start="1277" data-end="1295">technician working</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1296" data-end="1311">
<p data-start="1298" data-end="1311">shop exterior</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1312" data-end="1331">
<p data-start="1314" data-end="1331">finished vehicles</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1333" data-end="1398">Collision shops get <strong data-start="1353" data-end="1380">way more quote requests</strong> with real photos.</p>
<hr data-start="1400" data-end="1403">
<h3 data-start="1405" data-end="1441">3️⃣ Add the online estimate form</h3>
<p data-start="1442" data-end="1498">This is probably the <strong data-start="1463" data-end="1486">most valuable thing</strong> we can add.</p>
<p data-start="1500" data-end="1526">Customers will be able to:</p>
<ul data-start="1528" data-end="1607">
<li data-start="1528" data-end="1548">
<p data-start="1530" data-end="1548">enter vehicle info</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1549" data-end="1566">
<p data-start="1551" data-end="1566">describe damage</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1567" data-end="1582">
<p data-start="1569" data-end="1582">upload photos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1583" data-end="1607">
<p data-start="1585" data-end="1607">submit a quote request</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1609" data-end="1693">Those submissions appear in <strong data-start="1637" data-end="1692"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span> under “Forms”</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1695" data-end="1698">
<h1 data-start="1700" data-end="1746">One thing that would really improve the site</h1>
<p data-start="1747" data-end="1812">I’d strongly recommend adding a <strong data-start="1779" data-end="1811">Before / After repair slider</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1814" data-end="1882">Autobody shops that show transformation photos get a lot more trust.</p>
<p data-start="1884" data-end="1892">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1894" data-end="1946"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Before: smashed bumper</span><br><span>After: perfect repair</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1948" data-end="1983">Customer drags a slider to compare.</p>
<hr data-start="1985" data-end="1988">
<h3 data-start="1990" data-end="2029">Question for you before we continue</h3>
<p data-start="2030" data-end="2065">Do you want the website to include:</p>
<p data-start="2067" data-end="2155"><strong data-start="2067" data-end="2073">A)</strong> A <strong data-start="2076" data-end="2114">before/after repair slider gallery</strong><br data-start="2114" data-end="2117">
<strong data-start="2117" data-end="2123">B)</strong> A normal <strong data-start="2133" data-end="2155">photo gallery grid</strong></p>
<p data-start="2157" data-end="2235" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">The slider looks more professional, but I want to build it the way you prefer.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" a