<p data-start="721" data-end="805">Wait about <strong data-start="732" data-end="746">10 seconds</strong> for <strong data-start="751" data-end="792"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></strong> to redeploy.</p>
<p data-start="807" data-end="824">Refresh the page.</p>
<hr data-start="826" data-end="829">
