</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="387" data-end="433">So your site is now <strong data-start="407" data-end="432">fully live and stable</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="435" data-end="438">
<h2 data-start="440" data-end="467">Next thing we should fix</h2>
<p data-start="468" data-end="571">You mentioned earlier the <strong data-start="494" data-end="517">logo is still small</strong>. I looked at your screenshot again and I can see why.</p>
