t-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="9b0f45fb-cc14-40d5-83fa-b19bf86d4df3" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="149">Yes — that’s actually a <strong data-start="24" data-end="42">very good idea</strong> right now. Resetting the code will give us a <strong data-start="88" data-end="112">clean starting point</strong> so we’re not fighting earlier edits.</p>
<p data-start="151" data-end="287">Since your site is stored in <strong data-start="180" data-end="221"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span></strong>, the easiest way is to restore the original version of the files.</p>
<hr data-start="289" data-end="292">
<h1 data-start="294" data-end="352">Option 1 (Best): Restore the original files from history</h1>
<h3 data-start="354" data-end="382">1️⃣ Open your repository</h3>
<p data-start="383" data-end="409">Go to your repo and click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="411" data-end="429"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="431" data-end="434">
<h3 data-start="436" data-end="461">2️⃣ Click <strong data-start="450" data-end="461">History</strong></h3>
<p data-start="462" data-end="494">Near the top right you will see:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="496" data-end="511"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>History</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="513" data-end="522">Click it.</p>
<hr data-start="524" data-end="527">
<h3 data-start="529" data-end="560">3️⃣ Select the first commit</h3>
<p data-start="561" data-end="592">You will see a list of changes.</p>
<p data-start="594" data-end="659">Click the <strong data-start="604" data-end="623">earliest commit</strong> (the original version of the file).</p>
<hr data-start="661" data-end="664">
<h3 data-start="666" data-end="684">4️⃣ Restore it</h3>
<p data-start="685" data-end="767">Click the <strong data-start="695" data-end="714">three dots menu</strong> or the <strong data-start="722" data-end="739">revert option</strong>, then restore that version.</p>
<hr data-start="769" data-end="772">
<h3 data-start="774" data-end="800">5️⃣ Repeat for the CSS</h3>
<p data-start="801" data-end="823">Do the same steps for:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="825" data-end="854"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/css/styles.css</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="856" data-end="885">Restore the original version.</p>
<hr data-start="887" data-end="890">
<h1 data-start="892" data-end="945">Option 2 (Fastest): Upload the original files again</h1>
<p data-start="946" data-end="1013">If you still have the <strong data-start="968" data-end="996">original ZIP I generated</strong>, you can simply:</p>
<p data-start="1015" data-end="1064">1️⃣ Open the repo<br data-start="1032" data-end="1035">
2️⃣ Upload these files again:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1066" data-end="1106"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span><br><span>assets/css/styles.css</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1108" data-end="1126">3️⃣ Commit changes</p>
<p data-start="1128" data-end="1160">That overwrites the edited ones.</p>
<hr data-start="1162" data-end="1165">
<h1 data-start="1167" data-end="1191">What will happen after</h1>
<p data-start="1192" data-end="1218">Once you commit the reset:</p>
<ul data-start="1220" data-end="1342">
<li data-start="1220" data-end="1287">
<p data-start="1222" data-end="1287"><strong data-start="1222" data-end="1287"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span> redeploys automatically</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1288" data-end="1342">
<p data-start="1290" data-end="1342">Your site returns to the <strong data-start="1315" data-end="1342">clean original template</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1344" data-end="1361">Usually in about:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1363" data-end="1384"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>10–20 seconds</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1386" data-end="1389">
<h1 data-start="1391" data-end="1416">Why this is a good move</h1>
<p data-start="1417" data-end="1430">Right now we:</p>
<ul data-start="1432" data-end="1477">
<li data-start="1432" data-end="1450">
<p data-start="1434" data-end="1450">changed the logo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1451" data-end="1464">
<p data-start="1453" data-end="1464">edited HTML</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1465" data-end="1477">
<p data-start="1467" data-end="1477">edited CSS</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1479" data-end="1570">Resetting lets us rebuild the site <strong data-start="1514" data-end="1543">cleanly and intentionally</strong> instead of stacking fixes.</p>
<hr data-start="1572" data-end="1575">
<h1 data-start="1577" data-end="1611">What I recommend after the reset</h1>
<p data-start="1612" data-end="1659">We rebuild in this order (very clean workflow):</p>
<p data-start="1661" data-end="1804">1️⃣ Header + logo<br data-start="1678" data-end="1681">
2️⃣ Homepage hero section<br data-start="1706" data-end="1709">
3️⃣ Services section<br data-start="1729" data-end="1732">
4️⃣ Before/after gallery<br data-start="1756" data-end="1759">
5️⃣ Online estimate form<br data-start="1783" data-end="1786">
6️⃣ Google reviews</p>
<p data-start="1806" data-end="1865">That results in a <strong data-start="1824" data-end="1864">very professional autobody shop site</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1867" data-end="1870">
<h3 data-start="1872" data-end="1892">Before you reset</h3>
<p data-start="1893" data-end="2062" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Send me a screenshot of the <strong data-start="1921" data-end="1954">History page for <code data-start="1940" data-end="1952">index.html</code></strong>, and I’ll point to <strong data-start="1974" data-end="2009">exactly which commit to restore</strong> so we don’t accidentally remove something important.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="tr