d-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="4a3e0026-f2bc-41d5-b5af-e9cbee6618e2" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="155">Yes — and honestly that’s the <strong data-start="30" data-end="66">cleanest way to reset everything</strong> 👍<br data-start="69" data-end="72">
We’ll just <strong data-start="83" data-end="154">replace the entire repository contents with the original site files</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="157" data-end="195">This will remove any edits we made to:</p>
<ul data-start="197" data-end="268">
<li data-start="197" data-end="211">
<p data-start="199" data-end="211"><code data-start="199" data-end="211">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="212" data-end="226">
<p data-start="214" data-end="226"><code data-start="214" data-end="226">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="227" data-end="244">
<p data-start="229" data-end="244">logo references</p>
</li>
<li data-start="245" data-end="268">
<p data-start="247" data-end="268">anything else changed</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="270" data-end="360">Then <strong data-start="275" data-end="359"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span> will automatically redeploy the fresh site</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="362" data-end="365">
<h1 data-start="367" data-end="404">Easiest way to reset the repository</h1>
<h3 data-start="406" data-end="440">Step 1 — Open your GitHub repo</h3>
<p data-start="441" data-end="519">Go to the main page of your repo on <strong data-start="477" data-end="518"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span></strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="521" data-end="524">
<h3 data-start="526" data-end="557">Step 2 — Click <strong data-start="545" data-end="557">Add file</strong></h3>
<p data-start="559" data-end="576">Top right button:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="578" data-end="594"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Add file</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="596" data-end="608">Then choose:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="610" data-end="630"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Upload files</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="632" data-end="635">
<h3 data-start="637" data-end="680">Step 3 — Upload the clean website files</h3>
<p data-start="682" data-end="734">Upload the <strong data-start="693" data-end="727">entire original website folder</strong> again.</p>
<p data-start="736" data-end="752">You can drag in:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="754" data-end="820"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index.html</span><br><span>assets/</span><br><span>contact.html</span><br><span>gallery.html</span><br><span>services.html</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="822" data-end="853">GitHub will say something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="855" data-end="895"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>This will replace existing files</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="897" data-end="925">That’s exactly what we want.</p>
<hr data-start="927" data-end="930">
<h3 data-start="932" data-end="951">Step 4 — Commit</h3>
<p data-start="953" data-end="987">At the bottom type something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="989" data-end="1024"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Reset site to clean version</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1026" data-end="1037">Then click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1039" data-end="1061"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Commit changes</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1063" data-end="1066">
<h3 data-start="1068" data-end="1097">Step 5 — Wait for Netlify</h3>
<p data-start="1099" data-end="1112">Within about:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1114" data-end="1135"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>10–30 seconds</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1137" data-end="1182">Netlify will redeploy the site automatically.</p>
<p data-start="1184" data-end="1245">Your website will be <strong data-start="1205" data-end="1244">back to the clean starting template</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1247" data-end="1250">
<h1 data-start="1252" data-end="1268">After we reset</h1>
<p data-start="1269" data-end="1319">We’ll rebuild the site <strong data-start="1292" data-end="1318">properly in this order</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="1321" data-end="1471">1️⃣ Header + logo<br data-start="1338" data-end="1341">
2️⃣ Homepage hero section<br data-start="1366" data-end="1369">
3️⃣ Services section<br data-start="1389" data-end="1392">
4️⃣ Before/after repair gallery<br data-start="1423" data-end="1426">
5️⃣ Online estimate tool<br data-start="1450" data-end="1453">
6️⃣ Google reviews</p>
<p data-start="1473" data-end="1547">That workflow will give you a <strong data-start="1503" data-end="1546">very professional autobody shop website</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1549" data-end="1552">
<p data-start="1554" data-end="1765">💡 If you want, I can also give you a <strong data-start="1592" data-end="1644">much better starter template for collision shops</strong> than the one we began with. It looks more like a <strong data-start="1694" data-end="1731">$5k professional autobody website</strong> but still stays simple to manage.</p>
<p data-start="1767" data-end="1819" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Just say <strong data-start="1776" data-end="1797">“better template”</strong> and I’ll generate it.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-l