<p data-start="308" data-end="365">So in <code data-start="314" data-end="326">styles.css</code>, press <strong data-start="334" data-end="344">Ctrl+F</strong> and search for just:</p>
<p data-start="367" data-end="402"><strong data-start="367" data-end="382"><code data-start="369" data-end="380">site-logo</code></strong><br data-start="382" data-end="385">
(without the dot)</p>
<p data-start="404" data-end="421">If still nothing:</p>
<h3 data-start="423" data-end="460">2) Search for <code data-start="441" data-end="449">topbar</code> or <code data-start="453" data-end="460">brand</code></h3>
<p data-start="461" data-end="504">Press <strong data-start="467" data-end="477">Ctrl+F</strong> and search, one at a time:</p>
<ul data-start="506" data-end="604">
<li data-start="506" data-end="520">
<p data-start="508" data-end="520"><strong data-start="508" data-end="520"><code data-start="510" data-end="518">topbar</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="521" data-end="534">
<p data-start="523" data-end="534"><strong data-start="523" data-end="534"><code data-start="525" data-end="532">brand</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="535" data-end="577">
<p data-start="537" data-end="577"><strong data-start="537" data-end="547"><code data-start="539" data-end="545">logo</code></strong> (this one is broad but works)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="578" data-end="592">
<p data-start="580" data-end="592"><strong data-start="580" data-end="592"><code data-start="582" data-end="590">header</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="593" data-end="604">
<p data-start="595" data-end="604"><strong data-start="595" data-end="604"><code data-start="597" data-end="602">nav</code></strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="606" data-end="662">You’re looking for a block that looks like any of these:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="664" data-end="767"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">site-logo</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">brand</span><span> </span><span class="ͼo">img</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">topbar</span><span> </span><span class="ͼo">img</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span class="ͼl">header</span><span> </span><span class="ͼo">img</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span class="ͼl">nav</span><span> </span><span class="ͼo">img</span><span> { ... }</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="769" data-end="833">3) If you find a rule that targets the logo image, change it</h3>
<p data-start="834" data-end="859">Set the height like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="861" data-end="898"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div 