<hr data-start="900" data-end="903">
<h2 data-start="905" data-end="960">If searching isn’t working (quick guaranteed method)</h2>
<p data-start="961" data-end="1051">Let’s add a new rule at the <strong data-start="989" data-end="1004">very bottom</strong> of <code data-start="1008" data-end="1020">styles.css</code> that will override everything:</p>
<ol data-start="1053" data-end="1107">
<li data-start="1053" data-end="1092">
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1092">Scroll to the bottom of <code data-start="1080" data-end="1092">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1093" data-end="1107">
<p data-start="1096" data-end="1107">Paste this:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1109" data-end="1219"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼe">/* --- logo size override --- */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">site-logo</span><span>{</span><br><span>  height: </span><span class="ͼj">90</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">!important</span><span>;</span><br><span>  width: </span><span class="ͼj">auto</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">!important</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="3" data-start="1221" data-end="1272">
<li data-start="1221" data-end="1242">
<p data-start="1224" data-end="1242"><strong data-start="1224" data-end="1242">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1243" data-end="1272">
<p data-start="1246" data-end="1272">Refresh the site (Ctrl+F5)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1274" data-end="1336">That will force it bigger even if another rule is fighting it.</p>
<hr data-start="1338" data-end="1341">
