<h1 data-start="954" data-end="1005">After that we’ll make the site look <em data-start="992" data-end="998">much</em> better</h1>
<p data-start="1007" data-end="1059">Next upgrades I recommend for <strong data-start="1037" data-end="1058">Bev’s Repair Inc.</strong>:</p>
