<p data-start="62" data-end="149">Now that the <strong data-start="75" data-end="99">logo sizing is fixed</strong>, your site is finally behaving the way it should.</p>
<p data-start="151" data-end="189">You’ve already done the hardest parts:</p>
<p data-start="191" data-end="283">✔ Domain connected<br data-start="209" data-end="212">
✔ Site deployed<br data-start="227" data-end="230">
✔ HTTPS working<br data-start="245" data-end="248">
✔ Repository clean<br data-start="266" data-end="269">
✔ Logo fixed</p>
<p data-start="285" data-end="322">That’s a <strong data-start="294" data-end="321">huge amount of progress</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="324" data-end="327">
<h2 data-start="329" data-end="395">Next things that will make the site look much more professional</h2>
<p data-start="397" data-end="452">Here’s the order I recommend for <strong data-start="430" data-end="451">Bev’s Repair Inc.</strong>:</p>
<h3 data-start="454" data-end="483">1️⃣ Add a real hero photo</h3>
<p data-start="484" data-end="581">Right now the top section would look much better with a <strong data-start="540" data-end="570">shop photo or repair photo</strong> behind it.</p>
<p data-start="583" data-end="628">Examples that work great for collision shops:</p>
<ul data-start="629" data-end="720">
<li data-start="629" data-end="649">
<p data-start="631" data-end="649">car in paint booth</p>
</li>
<li data-start="650" data-end="682">
<p data-start="652" data-end="682">technician sanding or painting</p>
</li>
<li data-start="683" data-end="704">
<p data-start="685" data-end="704">before/after repair</p>
</li>
<li data-start="705" data-end="720">
<p data-start="707" data-end="720">shop exterior</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="722" data-end="781">We’ll make it look like a <strong data-start="748" data-end="780">modern autobody shop website</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="783" data-end="786">
<h3 data-start="788" data-end="828">2️⃣ Replace the gallery placeholders</h3>
<p data-start="829" data-end="854">Your site currently uses:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="856" data-end="905"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>gallery-1.svg</span><br><span>gallery-2.svg</span><br><span>gallery-3.svg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="907" data-end="953">Instead we’ll add <strong data-start="925" data-end="947">real repair photos</strong> like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="955" data-end="1029"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>before-repair.jpg</span><br><span>after-repair.jpg</span><br><span>paint-work.jpg</span><br><span>frame-repair.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1031" data-end="1050">These will go into:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1052" data-end="1071"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/img/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1073" data-end="1076">
<h3 data-start="1078" data-end="1117">3️⃣ Add an <strong data-start="1093" data-end="1117">online estimate tool</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1118" data-end="1141">This is huge for shops.</p>
<p data-start="1143" data-end="1157">Customers can:</p>
<ul data-start="1159" data-end="1221">
<li data-start="1159" data-end="1171">
<p data-start="1161" data-end="1171">enter name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1172" data-end="1187">
<p data-start="1174" data-end="1187">enter vehicle</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1188" data-end="1205">
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1205">describe damage</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1206" data-end="1221">
<p data-start="1208" data-end="1221">upload photos</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1223" data-end="1247">Then it emails the shop.</p>
<p data-start="1249" data-end="1335">This works great with <strong data-start="1271" data-end="1318"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span> forms</strong>, which are free.</p>
<hr data-start="1337" data-end="1340">
<h3 data-start="1342" data-end="1368">4️⃣ Add Google reviews</h3>
<p data-start="1369" data-end="1434">We can embed your Google reviews automatically so the site shows:</p>
<p data-start="1436" data-end="1483">⭐ rating<br data-start="1444" data-end="1447">
⭐ customer comments<br data-start="1466" data-end="1469">
⭐ review count</p>
<p data-start="1485" data-end="1515">This builds <strong data-start="1497" data-end="1514">instant trust</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1517" data-end="1520">
<h2 data-start="1522" data-end="1578">One quick improvement we can do right now (2 minutes)</h2>
<p data-start="1580" data-end="1656">Increase the <strong data-start="1593" data-end="1619">header height slightly</strong> so the logo has more breathing room.</p>
<p data-start="1658" data-end="1689">Find this line in <code data-start="1676" data-end="1688">styles.css</code>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1691" data-end="1729"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">topbar</span><span>{</span><br><span>padding:</span><span class="ͼj">14</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">24</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span>;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1731" data-end="1744">Change it to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1746" data-end="1784"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><di