ead-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="60c2f7c6-d459-4c59-9483-9f86dab9b834" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="97">That’s totally fine 👍 — most shops don’t have before/after photos when they first launch a site.</p>
<p data-start="99" data-end="166">We can still make <strong data-start="117" data-end="134">bevsrepair.ca</strong> look professional without them.</p>
<h2 data-start="168" data-end="192">Best option right now</h2>
<p data-start="193" data-end="233">Use <strong data-start="197" data-end="224">3–4 general shop photos</strong> instead.</p>
<p data-start="235" data-end="264">Things that work really well:</p>
<ul data-start="266" data-end="365">
<li data-start="266" data-end="281">
<p data-start="268" data-end="281">shop exterior</p>
</li>
<li data-start="282" data-end="315">
<p data-start="284" data-end="315">technician working on a vehicle</p>
</li>
<li data-start="316" data-end="340">
<p data-start="318" data-end="340">vehicle in paint booth</p>
</li>
<li data-start="341" data-end="365">
<p data-start="343" data-end="365">clean finished vehicle</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="367" data-end="423">These still make the site feel <strong data-start="398" data-end="422">real and trustworthy</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="425" data-end="482">Later you can swap them with before/after photos anytime.</p>
<hr data-start="484" data-end="487">
<h2 data-start="489" data-end="511">Where the photos go</h2>
<p data-start="512" data-end="560">Your photos will go in this folder in your repo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="562" data-end="581"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/img/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="583" data-end="592">Examples:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="594" data-end="709"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/img/shop-front.jpg</span><br><span>assets/img/paint-booth.jpg</span><br><span>assets/img/repair-work.jpg</span><br><span>assets/img/finished-car.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="711" data-end="755">Then we update the gallery page to use them.</p>
<hr data-start="757" data-end="760">
<h2 data-start="762" data-end="811">Another really good thing we can add right now</h2>
<p data-start="812" data-end="874">Since you don’t have photos yet, the <strong data-start="849" data-end="870">next best upgrade</strong> is:</p>
<h3 data-start="876" data-end="903">Online Estimate Request</h3>
<p data-start="905" data-end="919">Customers can:</p>
<ul data-start="921" data-end="1008">
<li data-start="921" data-end="933">
<p data-start="923" data-end="933">Enter name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="934" data-end="953">
<p data-start="936" data-end="953">Enter phone/email</p>
</li>
<li data-start="954" data-end="974">
<p data-start="956" data-end="974">Enter vehicle info</p>
</li>
<li data-start="975" data-end="992">
<p data-start="977" data-end="992">Describe damage</p>
</li>
<li data-start="993" data-end="1008">
<p data-start="995" data-end="1008">Upload photos</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1070">This sends the request directly to <strong data-start="1045" data-end="1069"><a data-start="1047" data-end="1067" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer" rel="noopener">bevsrepair@gmail.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1072" data-end="1151">This works <strong data-start="1083" data-end="1104">free with Netlify</strong> and makes your website actually generate work.</p>
<hr data-start="1153" data-end="1156">
<h2 data-start="1158" data-end="1213">I also recommend one small upgrade for your homepage</h2>
<p data-start="1214" data-end="1258">Right now the hero text says something like:</p>
<p data-start="1260" data-end="1295"><strong data-start="1260" data-end="1295">Professional repairs done right</strong></p>
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1349">For a shop website, something stronger works better:</p>
<p data-start="1351" data-end="1359">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1361" data-end="1506"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Collision Repair • Mechanical Service • Glass Replacement</span><br><br><span>Serving Manitou &amp; surrounding area since 1979.</span><br><span>MPI Accredited Repair Facility.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1508" data-end="1558">That makes it feel <strong data-start="1527" data-end="1557">more established and local</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1560" data-end="1563">
<h2 data-start="1565" data-end="1603">My recommendation for the next step</h2>
<p data-start="1605" data-end="1711">Let's add the <strong data-start="1619" data-end="1643">online estimate form</strong>.<br data-start="1644" data-end="1647">
It takes about <strong data-start="1662" data-end="1675">5 minutes</strong> and makes the site way more useful.</p>
<p data-start="1713" data-end="1740">After that we can also add:</p>
<p data-start="1742" data-end="1822">⭐ Google reviews<br data-start="1758" data-end="1761">
⭐ Map to the shop<br data-start="1778" data-end="1781">
⭐ Business hours<br data-start="1797" data-end="1800">
⭐ Click-to-call button</p>
<p data-start="1824" data-end="1844">All simple upgrades.</p>
<hr data-start="1846" data-end="1849">
<p data-start="1851" data-end="1978" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you're up for it, I can show you the <strong data-start="1891" data-end="1977">next improvement that makes the site look 10× more professional in about 2 minutes</strong>.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button clas