Most professional sites are built <strong data-start="109" data-end="140">content first, photos later</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="143" data-end="269">Let’s get all the <strong data-start="161" data-end="213">important business information on the site first</strong>, then when you start taking photos we can drop them in.</p>
<hr data-start="271" data-end="274">
<h1 data-start="276" data-end="312">Step 1 — Add your shop information</h1>
<p data-start="314" data-end="404">We’ll update the homepage and contact page with the real details for <strong data-start="383" data-end="404">Bev’s Repair Inc.</strong></p>
<p data-start="406" data-end="443">From what I have saved for your shop:</p>
<p data-start="445" data-end="547"><strong data-start="445" data-end="466">Bev’s Repair Inc.</strong><br data-start="466" data-end="469">
13025 Rd 48W<br data-start="481" data-end="484">
Manitou, MB R0G 1G0<br data-start="503" data-end="506">
📞 204-242-2318<br data-start="521" data-end="524">
