<p data-start="1558" data-end="1568">Google map</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1569" data-end="1591">
<p data-start="1571" data-end="1591">click-to-call button</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1593" data-end="1596">
<h1 data-start="1598" data-end="1623">Step 5 — Add shop hours</h1>
<p data-start="1625" data-end="1640">Typical layout:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1642" data-end="1720"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="Toggle view" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Monday – Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM</span><br><span>Saturday: Closed</span><br><span>Sunday: Closed</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1722" data-end="1749">(You can adjust if needed.)</p>
<hr data-start="1751" data-end="1754">
<h1 data-start="1756" data-end="1787">Step 6 — Add “About the Shop”</h1>
<p data-start="1789" data-end="1862">Since Bev’s has been around since <strong data-start="1823" data-end="1831">1979</strong>, that’s a great trust builder.</p>
<p data-start="1864" data-end="1877">Example text:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1879" data-end="2165">
<p data-start="1881" data-end="2165">Bev’s Repair Inc. has proudly served Manitou and the surrounding communities since 1979. As an MPI accredited repair facility, we provide professional collision repair, mechanical service, and automotive glass replacement with a focus on quality workmanship and customer satisfaction.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2167" data-end="2170">
<h1 data-start="2172" data-end="2211">Step 7 — Add an estimate request form</h1>
<p data-start="2213" data-end="2242">This will allow customers to:</p>
<ul data-start="2244" data-end="2299">
<li data-start="2244" data-end="2265">
<p data-start="2246" data-end="2265">submit vehicle info</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2266" data-end="2283">
<p data-start="2268" data-end="2283">describe damage</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2284" data-end="2299">
<p data-start="2286" data-end="2299">attach photos</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2301" data-end="2373">This is one of the <strong data-start="2320" data-end="2372">most valuable features for a repair shop website</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2375" data-end="2396">We can add that next.</p>
<hr data-start="2398" data-end="2401">
<h1 data-start="2403" data-end="2430">What I suggest we do next</h1>
<p data-start="2432" data-end="2473">Let’s add these sections to the homepage:</p>
<p data-start="2475" data-end="2601">1️⃣ <strong data-start="2479" data-end="2501">About Bev’s Repair</strong><br data-start="2501" data-end="2504">
2️⃣ <strong data-start="2508" data-end="2529">Services overview</strong><br data-start="2529" data-end="2532">
3️⃣ <strong data-start="2536" data-end="2564">Customer reviews section</strong><br data-start="2564" data-end="2567">
4️⃣ <strong data-start="2571" data-end="2601">Request an estimate button</strong></p>
<p data-start="2603" data-end="2669">That will make the homepage look <strong data-start="2636" data-end="2668">complete even without photos</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2671" data-end="2674">
<p data-start="2676" data-end="2925" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you're ready, the <strong data-start="2697" data-end="2767">next thing I can do is generate the exact homepage content for you</strong> so you can paste it directly into <code data-start="2802" data-end="2814">index.html</code>. It will be written specifically for <strong data-start="2852" data-end="2873">Bev’s Repair Inc.</strong> and will make the site feel much more professional.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8