<p data-start="1219" data-end="1311"><strong data-start="1219" data-end="1288"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span> will redeploy automatically</strong> (about 10–15 seconds).</p>
