roup-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="39220296-690f-4960-9046-5317ad05bb42" data-testid="conversation-turn-150" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="dd516406-d5e9-41c3-b2de-8b19c4ee0398" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="126">Don’t worry — this is <strong data-start="22" data-end="61">very common with Netlify free plans</strong>, and it’s usually easy to fix. Nothing is broken with your site.</p>
<p data-start="128" data-end="178">Most likely you hit one of these temporary limits:</p>
<ul data-start="180" data-end="244">
<li data-start="180" data-end="199">
<p data-start="182" data-end="199"><strong data-start="182" data-end="199">Build minutes</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="200" data-end="222">
<p data-start="202" data-end="222"><strong data-start="202" data-end="222">Deploy frequency</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="223" data-end="244">
<p data-start="225" data-end="244"><strong data-start="225" data-end="244">Bandwidth spike</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="246" data-end="372">Since we’ve been committing changes quickly while editing the site, Netlify probably triggered the <strong data-start="345" data-end="371">build limit protection</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="374" data-end="478">The good news: <strong data-start="389" data-end="420">your site will keep working</strong>. The limit only stops <strong data-start="443" data-end="458">new deploys</strong>, not the live site.</p>
<hr data-start="480" data-end="483">
<h1 data-start="485" data-end="507">First thing to check</h1>
<p data-start="508" data-end="565">Open <strong data-start="513" data-end="554"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></strong> and go to:</p>
<p data-start="567" data-end="588"><strong data-start="567" data-end="588">Project → Deploys</strong></p>
<p data-start="590" data-end="652">Look at the latest deploy message. It will say something like:</p>
<ul data-start="654" data-end="724">
<li data-start="654" data-end="680">
<p data-start="656" data-end="680"><em data-start="656" data-end="680">Build minutes exceeded</em></p>
</li>
<li data-start="681" data-end="701">
<p data-start="683" data-end="701"><em data-start="683" data-end="701">Too many deploys</em></p>
</li>
<li data-start="702" data-end="724">
<p data-start="704" data-end="724"><em data-start="704" data-end="724">Bandwidth exceeded</em></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="726" data-end="803">Tell me <strong data-start="734" data-end="760">which message it shows</strong>, because the fix depends on the exact one.</p>
<hr data-start="805" data-end="808">
<h1 data-start="810" data-end="851">Most common fix (very likely your case)</h1>
<p data-start="852" data-end="904">If it says <strong data-start="863" data-end="887">deploy limit reached</strong>, you can simply:</p>
<h3 data-start="906" data-end="938">Wait about <strong data-start="921" data-end="938">10–30 minutes</strong></h3>
<p data-start="940" data-end="1025">Netlify temporarily pauses deploys if there are <strong data-start="988" data-end="1024">too many commits in a short time</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1027" data-end="1068">After that you can deploy again normally.</p>
<hr data-start="1070" data-end="1073">
<h1 data-start="1075" data-end="1108">Another possibility (quick fix)</h1>
<p data-start="1109" data-end="1144">Sometimes the deploy is just stuck.</p>
<p data-start="1146" data-end="1152">Go to:</p>
<p data-start="1154" data-end="1196"><strong data-start="1154" data-end="1196">Deploys → Trigger deploy → Deploy site</strong></p>
<p data-start="1198" data-end="1220">This forces a rebuild.</p>
<hr data-start="1222" data-end="1225">
<h1 data-start="1227" data-end="1244">Important thing</h1>
<p data-start="1245" data-end="1272">Even if deploys are paused:</p>
<p data-start="1274" data-end="1340">Your site <strong data-start="1284" data-end="1301">bevsrepair.ca</strong> will still work normally for visitors.</p>
<hr data-start="1342" data-end="1345">
<h1 data-start="1347" data-end="1366">Also good to know</h1>
<p data-start="1367" data-end="1464">Your site is <strong data-start="1380" data-end="1394">very small</strong>, so normally you should <em data-start="1419" data-end="1426">never</em> hit the free limits for real traffic.</p>
<p data-start="1466" data-end="1501">This only happened because we were:</p>
<ul data-start="1503" data-end="1553">
<li data-start="1503" data-end="1512">
<p data-start="1505" data-end="1512">editing</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1513" data-end="1525">
<p data-start="1515" data-end="1525">committing</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1526" data-end="1537">
<p data-start="1528" data-end="1537">deploying</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1538" data-end="1553">
<p data-start="1540" data-end="1553">editing again</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1555" data-end="1568">very quickly.</p>
<hr data-start="1570" data-end="1573">
<h1 data-start="1575" data-end="1590">While we wait</h1>
<p data-start="1591" data-end="1612">We can still work on:</p>
<ul data-start="1614" data-end="1683">
<li data-start="1614" data-end="1634">
<p data-start="1616" data-end="1634">Services page text</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1635" data-end="1654">
<p data-start="1637" data-end="1654">Contact page info</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1655" data-end="1667">
<p data-start="1657" data-end="1667">Shop hours</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1668" data-end="1683">
<p data-start="1670" data-end="1683">About section</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1685" data-end="1731">Those edits will deploy once the limit resets.</p>
<hr data-start="1733" data-end="1736">
<p data-start="1738" data-end="1858" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, send a screenshot of the <strong data-start="1776" data-end="1801">Netlify error message</strong>, and I’ll tell you <strong data-start="1821" data-end="1857">exactly what triggered the limit</strong>.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#2126ae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Share" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" id="radix-_r_3it_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="cursor-pointer touch:px-2.5 text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary h-[30px] rounded-md px-1.5" aria-label="Switch model"><div class="flex items-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ec66f0" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="More actions" type="button" id="radix-_r_nc_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="b6bb2fb3-106f-4cb6-9de1-0762cd2d29da" data-testid="conversation-turn-151" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h5 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="b6bb2fb3-106f-4cb6-9de1-0762cd2d29da" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">it says i exceeded credit limits</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="b7e21912-ea1f-43d0-b2f0-21535a407c7c" data-testid="conversation-turn-152" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="b7e21912-ea1f-43d0-b2f0-21535a407c7c" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="217">Got it — <strong data-start="9" data-end="37">“exceeded credit limits”</strong> on <strong data-start="41" data-end="82"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Netlify</span></span></strong> usually means the account’s <strong data-start="111" data-end="163">free usage credit for the billing period was hit</strong>, so Netlify temporarily stops <strong data-start="194" data-end="216">new builds/deploys</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="219" data-end="245">The important thing first:</p>
<p data-start="247" data-end="358"><strong data-start="247" data-end="281">Your website will stay online.</strong><br data-start="281" data-end="284">
Visitors can still use <strong data-start="307" data-end="324">bevsrepair.ca</strong>. Only <strong data-start="331" data-end="346">new deploys</strong> are paused.</p>
<hr data-start="360" data-end="363">
<h2 data-start="365" data-end="391">What probably caused it</h2>
<p data-start="392" data-end="417">Most likely one of these:</p>
<ol data-start="419" data-end="559">
<li data-start="419" data-end="485">
<p data-start="422" data-end="485"><strong data-start="422" data-end="454">Many deploys in a short time</strong> (we did a lot while editing)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="486" data-end="522">
<p data-start="489" data-end="522"><strong data-start="489" data-end="520">Build minutes limit reached</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="523" data-end="559">
<p data-start="526" data-end="559"><strong data-start="526" data-end="559">Bandwidth spike during builds</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="561" data-end="669">Small sites like yours almost never exceed bandwidth — it’s usually <strong data-start="629" data-end="668">build minutes from repeated deploys</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="671" data-end="674">
<h1 data-start="676" data-end="693">The quick fixes</h1>
<h3 data-start="695" data-end="736">Option 1 — Wait for the monthly reset</h3>
<p data-start="737" data-end="780">Netlify free plans reset usage <strong data-start="768" data-end="779">monthly</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="782" data-end="876">If you just crossed the limit, deploys will start working again when the billing cycle resets.</p>
<hr data-start="878" data-end="881">
<h3 data-start="883" data-end="941">Option 2 — Add a small credit card limit (recommended)</h3>
<p data-start="942" data-end="1014">You can add a payment method but <strong data-start="975" data-end="1013">set a $0 or very small spend limit</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1016" data-end="1022">Steps:</p>
<ol data-start="1024" data-end="1122">
<li data-start="1024" data-end="1054">
<p data-start="1027" data-end="1054">Go to <strong data-start="1033" data-end="1054">Netlify → Billing</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1055" data-end="1086">
<p data-start="1058" data-end="1086">Click <strong data-start="1064" data-end="1086">Add payment method</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1087" data-end="1122">
<p data-start="1090" data-end="1122">Set a <strong data-start="1096" data-end="1109">spend cap</strong> (example $5)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1124" data-end="1181">This unlocks deploys again but prevents surprise charges.</p>
<p data-start="1183" data-end="1279">For a small static site like yours, you will almost certainly <strong data-start="1245" data-end="1278">never actually hit paid usage</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1281" data-end="1284">
<h3 data-start="1286" data-end="1334">Option 3 — Stop automatic builds temporarily</h3>
<p data-start="1335" data-end="1396">Since your site is already live, we can slow down deploys by:</p>
<ul data-start="1398" data-end="1442">
<li data-start="1398" data-end="1415">
<p data-start="1400" data-end="1415">editing locally</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1416" data-end="1442">
<p data-start="1418" data-end="1442">committing fewer changes</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1444" data-end="1479">This prevents hitting limits again.</p>
<hr data-start="1481" data-end="1484">
<h1 data-start="1486" data-end="1509">Important reassurance</h1>
<p data-start="1510" data-end="1544">Your site is <strong data-start="1523" data-end="1543">very lightweight</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="1546" data-end="1588">
<li data-start="1546" data-end="1559">
<p data-start="1548" data-end="1559">static HTML</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1560" data-end="1573">
<p data-start="1562" data-end="1573">no database</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1574" data-end="1588">
<p data-start="1576" data-end="1588">small images</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1590" data-end="1674">So once we finish building it, <strong data-start="1621" data-end="1673">Netlify free hosting is usually more than enough</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1676" data-end="1679">
<h1 data-start="1681" data-end="1732">Alternative (if you want completely free forever)</h1>
<p data-start="1733" data-end="1775">We could also host the exact same site on:</p>
<ul data-start="1777" data-end="1876">
<li data-start="1777" data-end="1826">
<p data-start="1779" data-end="1826"><strong data-start="1779" data-end="1826"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Cloudflare</span></span> Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1827" data-end="1876">
<p data-start="1829" data-end="1876"><strong data-start="1829" data-end="1876"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span> Pages</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1878" data-end="1922">Both are <strong data-start="1887" data-end="1921">unlimited for sites like yours</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1924" data-end="1964">But I wouldn’t switch yet unless needed.</p>
<hr data-start="1966" data-end="1969">
<h1 data-start="1971" data-end="1999">What I recommend right now</h1>
<ol data-start="2000" data-end="2088">
<li data-start="2000" data-end="2037">
<p data-start="2003" data-end="2037">Open <strong data-start="2008" data-end="2037">Netlify → Billing → Usage</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2038" data-end="2088">
<p data-start="2041" data-end="2088">Tell me <strong data-start="2049" data-end="2088">which category hit the credit limit</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="2090" data-end="2117">It will say something like:</p>
<ul data-start="2119" data-end="2168">
<li data-start="2119" data-end="2134">
<p data-start="2121" data-end="2134">Build minutes</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2135" data-end="2146">
<p data-start="2137" data-end="2146">Bandwidth</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2147" data-end="2158">
<p data-start="2149" data-end="2158">Functions</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2159" data-end="2168">
<p data-start="2161" data-end="2168">Deploys</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2170" data-end="2248" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Once I know that, I can tell you <strong data-start="2203" data-end="2247">exactly how to fix it in about 2 minutes</strong>.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-se