in)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="4d169038-30c9-4558-9401-6fd5f79d1021" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="55">Yes — <strong data-start="6" data-end="52">you can absolutely keep editing right now.</strong> 👍</p>
<p data-start="57" data-end="138">DNS changes only affect <strong data-start="81" data-end="116">how the domain reaches the site</strong>, not the site itself.</p>
<p data-start="140" data-end="293">Your site is already being served by <strong data-start="177" data-end="224"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span> Pages</strong>, so any edits you make in the repository will still deploy normally.</p>
<hr data-start="295" data-end="298">
<h2 data-start="300" data-end="333">What happens while DNS updates</h2>
<p data-start="334" data-end="394">Right now there are basically <strong data-start="364" data-end="393">two possible access paths</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="396" data-end="453">1️⃣ <strong data-start="400" data-end="424">GitHub Pages address</strong> (always works immediately)</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="454" data-end="507"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://bevsrepair.github.io/bevsrepair-site/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="509" data-end="535">2️⃣ <strong data-start="513" data-end="535">Your custom domain</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="536" data-end="565"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://bevsrepair.ca</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="567" data-end="628">The second one will start working once DNS finishes updating.</p>
<hr data-start="630" data-end="633">
<h2 data-start="635" data-end="657">When you edit files</h2>
<p data-start="658" data-end="687">If you change something like:</p>
<ul data-start="689" data-end="736">
<li data-start="689" data-end="703">
<p data-start="691" data-end="703"><code data-start="691" data-end="703">index.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="704" data-end="721">
<p data-start="706" data-end="721"><code data-start="706" data-end="721">services.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="722" data-end="736">
<p data-start="724" data-end="736"><code data-start="724" data-end="736">styles.css</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="738" data-end="786">and click <strong data-start="748" data-end="766">Commit changes</strong>, GitHub Pages will:</p>
<ol data-start="788" data-end="833">
<li data-start="788" data-end="807">
<p data-start="791" data-end="807">rebuild the site</p>
</li>
<li data-start="808" data-end="833">
<p data-start="811" data-end="833">redeploy automatically</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="835" data-end="868">Usually within <strong data-start="850" data-end="867">30–60 seconds</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="870" data-end="873">
<h2 data-start="875" data-end="910">Good workflow while DNS finishes</h2>
<p data-start="911" data-end="935">You can keep working on:</p>
<ul data-start="937" data-end="1026">
<li data-start="937" data-end="960">
<p data-start="939" data-end="960">Services descriptions</p>
</li>
<li data-start="961" data-end="982">
<p data-start="963" data-end="982">Contact information</p>
</li>
<li data-start="983" data-end="995">
<p data-start="985" data-end="995">Shop hours</p>
</li>
<li data-start="996" data-end="1011">
<p data-start="998" data-end="1011">About section</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1012" data-end="1026">
<p data-start="1014" data-end="1026">Reviews page</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1028" data-end="1061">Everything will publish normally.</p>
<p data-start="1063" data-end="1154">When DNS finishes, <strong data-start="1082" data-end="1153">bevsrepair.ca will simply point to the latest version automatically</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1156" data-end="1159">
<h2 data-start="1161" data-end="1196">One small thing I recommend next</h2>
<p data-start="1197" data-end="1259">Before we continue editing a lot, we should add one tiny file:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1261" data-end="1278"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.nojekyll</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1280" data-end="1381">This prevents GitHub Pages from trying to process your site as a blog and avoids random issues later.</p>
<p data-start="1383" data-end="1420">It takes about <strong data-start="1398" data-end="1412">10 seconds</strong> to add.</p>
<hr data-start="1422" data-end="1425">
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1542">If you want, next we can also add <strong data-start="1461" data-end="1541">three things that will immediately make the site look much more professional</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="1544" data-end="1673">1️⃣ Google Maps directions button<br data-start="1577" data-end="1580">
2️⃣ Shop hours that show <strong data-start="1605" data-end="1636">Open / Closed automatically</strong><br data-start="1636" data-end="1639">
3️⃣ A <strong data-start="1645" data-end="1668">Request an Estimate</strong> form</p>
<p data-start="1675" data-end="1763" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Those are the <strong data-start="1689" data-end="1732">three biggest things customers look for</strong> on a repair shop website. 🚗🔧</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-tok