<h2 data-start="75" data-end="134">Step 1 — Update the shop details (fast + most important)</h2>
<p data-start="135" data-end="217">Open <strong data-start="140" data-end="163"><code data-start="142" data-end="161">content/site.json</code></strong> (or <strong data-start="168" data-end="191"><code data-start="170" data-end="189">content/home.json</code></strong> if you see that instead).</p>
<p data-start="219" data-end="319">If you tell me which one you see in the <code data-start="259" data-end="268">content</code> folder, I’ll tell you exactly which file to click.</p>
<h3 data-start="321" data-end="346">Put these details in:</h3>
<ul data-start="347" data-end="566">
<li data-start="347" data-end="385">
<p data-start="349" data-end="385"><strong data-start="349" data-end="367">Business name:</strong> Bev’s Repair Inc.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="386" data-end="434">
<p data-start="388" data-end="434"><strong data-start="388" data-end="400">Address:</strong> 13025 Rd 48W, Manitou, MB R0G 1G0</p>
</li>
<li data-start="435" data-end="460">
<p data-start="437" data-end="460"><strong data-start="437" data-end="447">Phone:</strong> 204-242-2318</p>
</li>
<li data-start="461" data-end="494">
<p data-start="463" data-end="494"><strong data-start="463" data-end="473">Email:</strong> <a data-start="474" data-end="494" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer" rel="noopener">bevsrepair@gmail.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="495" data-end="566">
<p data-start="497" data-end="566"><strong data-start="497" data-end="518">Tagline/services:</strong> Collision • Mechanical • Glass (MPI Accredited)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="568" data-end="801">✅ <strong data-start="570" data-end="599">Question for you (quick):</strong><br data-start="599" data-end="602">
In your repo, open the <strong data-start="625" data-end="636">content</strong> folder — what files are inside? (ex: <code data-start="674" data-end="685">site.json</code>, <code data-start="687" data-end="698">home.json</code>, <code data-start="700" data-end="712">hours.json</code>, etc.)<br data-start="719" data-end="722">
Just type the filenames you see and I’ll guide you click-by-click what to edit.</p>
<hr data-start="803" data-end="806">
<h2 data-start="808" data-end="882">While you’re looking, here’s the next 3 “details” we’ll add after that:</h2>
<h3 data-start="883" data-end="917">Step 2 — Services page wording</h3>
<p data-start="918" data-end="1015">I’ll give you a clean professional list (collision, paint, frame, mechanical, glass, ADAS scans).</p>
<h3 data-start="1017" data-end="1042">Step 3 — Contact page</h3>
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1106">Add address + click-to-call + email + hours + Google Maps link.</p>
<h3 data-start="1108" data-end="1137">Step 4 — Homepage buttons</h3>
<p data-start="1138" data-end="1148">Make sure:</p>
<ul data-start="1149" data-end="1265">
<li data-start="1149" data-end="1178">
<p data-start="1151" data-end="1178"><strong data-start="1151" data-end="1163">Call Now</strong> actually calls</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1179" data-end="1217">
<p data-start="1181" data-end="1217"><strong data-start="1181" data-end="1199">Get Directions</strong> opens Google Maps</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1218" data-end="1265">
<p data-start="1220" data-end="1265"><strong data-start="1220" data-end="1239">Request a Quote</strong> goes to the estimate form</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1267" data-end="1343" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Send me the filenames in the <strong data-start="1296" data-end="1307">content</strong> folder and we’ll start with Step 1.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-seco