It already follows the correct format and will work immediately when you commit it.</p>
<p data-start="178" data-end="232">Just <strong data-start="183" data-end="221">replace everything inside the file</strong> with this.</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="234" data-end="1230"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>[</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    "name": </span><span class="ͼk">"Mark D."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "rating": </span><span class="ͼj">5</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "text": </span><span class="ͼk">"Excellent repair work and very professional service. The vehicle looked like new when it was finished and the communication throughout the process was great."</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    "name": </span><span class="ͼk">"Lisa P."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "rating": </span><span class="ͼj">5</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "text": </span><span class="ͼk">"Bev's Repair did an amazing job fixing the damage on my vehicle. The paint match was perfect and the turnaround time was faster than expected."</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    "name": </span><span class="ͼk">"Ryan T."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "rating": </span><span class="ͼj">5</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "text": </span><span class="ͼk">"Very friendly and knowledgeable staff. They explained the repair process clearly and the final result exceeded my expectations."</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    "name": </span><span class="ͼk">"Jessica M."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "rating": </span><span class="ͼj">5</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "text": </span><span class="ͼk">"Highly recommend Bev's Repair. Honest shop, quality workmanship, and great customer service."</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    "name": </span><span class="ͼk">"Chris B."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "rating": </span><span class="ͼj">5</span><span>,</span><br><span>    "text": </span><span class="ͼk">"Professional and reliable service from start to finish. The repair was completed on time and the vehicle looked perfect when I picked it up."</span><br><span>  }</span><br><span>]</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1232" data-end="1251">After you paste it:</p>
<ol data-start="1253" data-end="1345">
<li data-start="1253" data-end="1280">
<p data-start="1256" data-end="1280">Click <strong data-start="1262" data-end="1280">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1281" data-end="1312">
<p data-start="1284" data-end="1312">Wait about <strong data-start="1295" data-end="1312">30–40 seconds</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1313" data-end="1345">
<p data-start="1316" data-end="1345">Refresh your <strong data-start="1329" data-end="1345">Reviews page</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1347" data-end="1399">You should now see <strong data-start="1366" data-end="1398">5 customer reviews displayed</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1401" data-end="1404">
<h3 data-start="1406" data-end="1419">Small tip</h3>
<p data-start="1420" data-end="1496">These are <strong data-start="1430" data-end="1449">starter reviews</strong> so the page doesn’t look empty. Later you can:</p>
<ul data-start="1498" data-end="1595">
<li data-start="1498" data-end="1541">
<p data-start="1500" data-end="1541">replace them with <strong data-start="1518" data-end="1541">real Google reviews</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1542" data-end="1560">
<p data-start="1544" data-end="1560">add more entries</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1561" data-end="1595">
<p data-start="1563" data-end="1595">add reviewer photos if you want.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1597" data-end="1600">
<p data-start="1602" data-end="1701">Next, I recommend we quickly add <strong data-start="1635" data-end="1700">one thing that will make the site look much more professional</strong>:</p>
