<hr data-start="1483" data-end="1486">
<h3 data-start="1488" data-end="1532">Small improvement I recommend after this</h3>
<p data-start="1533" data-end="1619">Once services are in, the next <strong data-start="1564" data-end="1614">two things that make the website look finished</strong> are:</p>
<p data-start="1621" data-end="1718">1️⃣ <strong data-start="1625" data-end="1658">Google Maps Directions button</strong><br data-start="1658" data-end="1661">
2️⃣ <strong data-start="1665" data-end="1718">Call Now button that dials the shop automatically</strong></p>
<p data-start="1720" data-end="1805">Both take about <strong data-start="1736" data-end="1755">1 minute to add</strong> and dramatically improve usability for customers.</p>
