m] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="0358e4a0-b2c5-4648-bdd9-e2796c030b03" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="141">Good question — and <strong data-start="20" data-end="27">yes</strong>, if your <code data-start="37" data-end="52">services.json</code> file currently has a <strong data-start="74" data-end="93"><code data-start="76" data-end="83">cards</code> section</strong>, the services need to go <strong data-start="119" data-end="140">inside that array</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="143" data-end="196">Your file likely looks something like this structure:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="198" data-end="235"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span>  "cards": [</span><br><span>    </span><br><span>  ]</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="237" data-end="280">So the services go <strong data-start="256" data-end="279">inside the brackets</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="282" data-end="285">
<h1 data-start="287" data-end="317">Correct format for your file</h1>
<p data-start="319" data-end="361">Paste this <strong data-start="330" data-end="360">inside the <code data-start="343" data-end="350">cards</code> section</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="363" data-end="1536"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span>  "cards": [</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Collision Repair (MPI)"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "description": </span><span class="ͼk">"MPI accredited collision repairs restoring vehicles to manufacturer standards after accidents or damage."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Autobody Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "description": </span><span class="ͼk">"Professional dent repair, panel replacement, and structural body repairs."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Frame Straightening"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "description": </span><span class="ͼk">"Precision frame and structural alignment using professional frame straightening equipment."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Paint &amp; Refinishing"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "description": </span><span class="ͼk">"High-quality paint matching and refinishing for seamless factory-quality results."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Mechanical Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "description": </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics and mechanical repairs including engine, suspension, and general vehicle maintenance."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Auto Glass Replacement"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "description": </span><span class="ͼk">"Windshield and automotive glass replacement with proper sealing and installation."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics &amp; ADAS Scanning"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "description": </span><span class="ͼk">"Pre-scan and post-scan diagnostics including ADAS system calibration after repairs."</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>  ]</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1538" data-end="1543">Then:</p>
<p data-start="1545" data-end="1642">1️⃣ Click <strong data-start="1555" data-end="1573">Commit changes</strong><br data-start="1573" data-end="1576">
2️⃣ Wait about <strong data-start="1591" data-end="1605">30 seconds</strong><br data-start="1605" data-end="1608">
3️⃣ Refresh your <strong data-start="1625" data-end="1642">Services page</strong></p>
<p data-start="1644" data-end="1699">Your services should appear as <strong data-start="1675" data-end="1698">cards automatically</strong>.</p>
