<h3 data-start="146" data-end="180">Next steps (do these in order)</h3>
<ol data-start="182" data-end="216">
<li data-start="182" data-end="216">
<p data-start="185" data-end="216"><strong data-start="185" data-end="216">Commit the change in GitHub</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="217" data-end="374">
<li data-start="217" data-end="272">
<p data-start="219" data-end="272">Scroll to the bottom of the <code data-start="247" data-end="262">services.json</code> edit page</p>
</li>
<li data-start="273" data-end="332">
<p data-start="275" data-end="332">In the commit box, type something like: <code data-start="315" data-end="332">Update services</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="333" data-end="374">
<p data-start="335" data-end="374">Click <strong data-start="341" data-end="359">Commit changes</strong> (green button)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<ol start="2" data-start="376" data-end="412">
<li data-start="376" data-end="412">
