<p data-start="51" data-end="174">Your <strong data-start="56" data-end="123"><code data-start="58" data-end="73">services.html</code> is NOT loading <code data-start="89" data-end="112">content/services.json</code> directly</strong>.<br data-start="124" data-end="127">
It’s calling <strong data-start="140" data-end="160"><code data-start="142" data-end="158">initServices()</code></strong> on this line:</p>
<ul data-start="176" data-end="215">
<li data-start="176" data-end="215">
<p data-start="178" data-end="215"><strong data-start="178" data-end="191">Line ~59:</strong> <code data-start="192" data-end="215">await initServices();</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="217" data-end="313">And <code data-start="221" data-end="237">initServices()</code> lives in <strong data-start="247" data-end="271"><code data-start="249" data-end="269">/assets/js/site.js</code></strong> (the last line shows it loads that file).</p>
<p data-start="315" data-end="454">So your services aren’t showing because the problem is in <strong data-start="373" data-end="396"><code data-start="375" data-end="394">assets/js/site.js</code></strong> (wrong path, wrong JSON shape, or it’s failing silently).</p>
<hr data-start="456" data-end="459">
<h2 data-start="461" data-end="499">What to do right now (2-minute fix)</h2>
<h3 data-start="501" data-end="553">1) Open the file that actually controls Services</h3>
<p data-start="554" data-end="668">Go to:<br>
<strong data-start="561" data-end="584"><code data-start="563" data-end="582">assets/js/site.js</code></strong><br data-start="584" data-end="587">
Then <strong data-start="592" data-end="602">Ctrl+F</strong> and search: <strong data-start="615" data-end="642"><code data-start="617" data-end="640">function initServices</code></strong> (or just <code data-start="652" data-end="666">initServices</code>).</p>
<h3 data-start="670" data-end="718">2) In that function, look for the fetch line</h3>
<p data-start="719" data-end="749">You should see something like:</p>
<ul data-start="750" data-end="815">
<li data-start="750" data-end="782">
<p data-start="752" data-end="782"><code data-start="752" data-end="779">fetch('...services.json')</code><br>
or</p>
</li>
<li data-start="783" data-end="815">
<p data-start="785" data-end="815"><code data-start="785" data-end="815">loadJSON('...services.json')</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="817" data-end="852">✅ <strong data-start="819" data-end="852">Make sure it is exactly this:</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="853" data-end="893"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼm">fetch</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼk">'content/services.json'</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="895" data-end="1000">(If it says <code data-start="907" data-end="931">/content/services.json</code> or <code data-start="935" data-end="960">./content/services.json</code>, change it to <code data-start="975" data-end="998">content/services.json</code>.)</p>
<h3 data-start="1002" data-end="1072">3) Make it accept either JSON format (prevents this issue forever)</h3>
<p data-start="1073" data-end="1139">Right after it does <code data-start="1093" data-end="1115">.then(r =&gt; r.json())</code>, make sure it has this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1141" data-end="1184"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼg">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">cards</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">data</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>cards </span><span class="ͼg">||</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">data</span><span>;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1186" data-end="1230">So the whole block should look roughly like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1232" data-end="1346"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼg">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">await</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">fetch</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼk">'content/services.json'</span><span>)</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>then(</span><span class="ͼm">r</span><span> =&gt; </span><span class="ͼm">r</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>json());</span><br><span class="ͼg">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">cards</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">data</span><span class="ͼg">.</span><span>cards </span><span class="ͼg">||</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">data</span><span>;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1348" data-end="1402">Then it should loop <code data-start="1368" data-end="1388">cards.forEach(...)</code> (or similar).</p>
<hr data-start="1404" data-end="1407">
