radix-_r_1g7_" data-state="closed" class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg w-full h-full max-w-96 max-h-64" aria-label="Open image in full view"><img alt="Uploaded image" width="4080" height="3060" class="max-w-full object-cover object-center overflow-hidden rounded-lg w-full h-full max-w-96 max-h-64 w-fit transition-opacity duration-300 opacity-100" src="./shop-hero_files/image-1772662353414.jpg"></button></div></div></div></div><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 rounded-se-lg max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Still blank </div></div></div></div><div class="text-token-text-secondary my-2 me-4 flex flex-row justify-end gap-1 text-xs"></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="1c92965e-38fa-48aa-97d7-ecd70b851ed7" data-testid="conversation-turn-190" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="5ab138f4-24a6-4ff1-afb2-292e7b6eb4b9" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="148">Got it — this tells us the page <strong data-start="32" data-end="57">is loading the layout</strong>, but the <strong data-start="67" data-end="107">services cards aren’t being injected</strong>, which almost always means one of these:</p>
<ol data-start="150" data-end="342">
<li data-start="150" data-end="227">
<p data-start="153" data-end="227"><code data-start="153" data-end="176">content/services.json</code> <strong data-start="177" data-end="200">isn’t being fetched</strong> (404 / wrong path), <strong data-start="221" data-end="227">or</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="228" data-end="342">
<p data-start="231" data-end="342">the JSON loads but the <strong data-start="254" data-end="277">shape doesn’t match</strong> what the code expects (<code data-start="301" data-end="317">services.cards</code>), so it injects nothing.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="344" data-end="384">Let’s fix it in the fastest, surest way.</p>
<hr data-start="386" data-end="389">
<h2 data-start="391" data-end="444">Step 1 — Quick test: open the JSON in your browser</h2>
<p data-start="445" data-end="465">In a new tab, go to:</p>
<p data-start="467" data-end="514"><strong data-start="467" data-end="514"><a data-start="469" data-end="512" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://bevsrepair.ca/content/services.json<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></strong></p>
<h3 data-start="516" data-end="538">What should happen</h3>
<p data-start="539" data-end="568">You should see raw JSON text.</p>
<ul data-start="570" data-end="696">
<li data-start="570" data-end="662">
<p data-start="572" data-end="662">If you get <strong data-start="583" data-end="610">404 / Not Found / blank</strong> → the file isn’t publishing where the code expects.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="663" data-end="696">
<p data-start="665" data-end="696">If you see JSON → go to Step 2.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="698" data-end="787">(Do the same check for <code data-start="721" data-end="735">gallery.json</code> and <code data-start="740" data-end="754">reviews.json</code> later, but start with services.)</p>
<hr data-start="789" data-end="792">
<h2 data-start="794" data-end="848">Step 2 — Make sure <code data-start="816" data-end="831">services.json</code> matches the code</h2>
<p data-start="849" data-end="866">Your JS is doing:</p>
<ul data-start="868" data-end="965">
<li data-start="868" data-end="886">
<p data-start="870" data-end="886"><code data-start="870" data-end="886">services.intro</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="887" data-end="914">
<p data-start="889" data-end="914"><code data-start="889" data-end="914">services.cards.map(...)</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="915" data-end="965">
<p data-start="917" data-end="965">inside each card: <code data-start="935" data-end="944">c.title</code>, <code data-start="946" data-end="954">c.desc</code>, <code data-start="956" data-end="965">c.items</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="967" data-end="1041">So your <code data-start="975" data-end="998">content/services.json</code> must look <strong data-start="1009" data-end="1040">exactly like this structure</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1043" data-end="2943"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span>  "intro": </span><span class="ͼk">"MPI-accredited collision repair, autobody, mechanical, glass, and diagnostics."</span><span>,</span><br><span>  "cards": [</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Collision Repair (MPI)"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Accident repairs handled start to finish with clear communication and quality control."</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "items": [</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Claims support &amp; documentation"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Structural &amp; cosmetic repairs"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Paint match &amp; refinishing"</span><br><span>      ]</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Autobody Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Bumpers, fenders, doors, panels, and full body repair."</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "items": [</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Dent repair &amp; filler work"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Panel replacement"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Fit &amp; finish checks"</span><br><span>      ]</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Frame Straightening"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Measured, pulled, and verified on frame equipment."</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "items": [</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Structural measurements"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Frame pulls &amp; corrections"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Post-repair verification"</span><br><span>      ]</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Paint &amp; Refinishing"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Prep, prime, paint, and polish for a clean OEM-style finish."</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "items": [</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Surface prep &amp; masking"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Color match"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Denib &amp; polish"</span><br><span>      ]</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Mechanical Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Mechanical service and repairs alongside collision work."</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "items": [</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"R&amp;R components as needed"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"General mechanical repairs"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Road test when applicable"</span><br><span>      ]</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Auto Glass Replacement"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Windshield and glass replacement with attention to seal and fit."</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "items": [</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Windshield replacement"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Glass R&amp;R"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Leak check"</span><br><span>      ]</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics &amp; ADAS Scanning"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Pre/post scans and ADAS-related checks when required."</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "items": [</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Pre-repair scan"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"Post-repair scan"</span><span>,</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼk">"ADAS verification (as required)"</span><br><span>      ]</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>  ]</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2945" data-end="3019">✅ Paste that <strong data-start="2958" data-end="2980">as the entire file</strong> in <code data-start="2984" data-end="3007">content/services.json</code> and commit.</p>
<hr data-start="3021" data-end="3024">
<h2 data-start="3026" data-end="3062">Step 3 — Hard refresh (important)</h2>
<p data-start="3063" data-end="3080">After committing:</p>
<ul data-start="3081" data-end="3165">
<li data-start="3081" data-end="3119">
<p data-start="3083" data-end="3119">Windows/Chrome: <strong data-start="3099" data-end="3119">Ctrl + Shift + R</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="3120" data-end="3165">
<p data-start="3122" data-end="3165">Or open the site in an <strong data-start="3145" data-end="3158">Incognito</strong> window</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3167" data-end="3200">GitHub Pages caches aggressively.</p>
<hr data-start="3202" data-end="3205">
<h2 data-start="3207" data-end="3246">If it STILL shows blank after Step 2</h2>
<p data-start="3247" data-end="3318">Then it’s almost certainly the script isn’t running on <code data-start="3302" data-end="3317">services.html</code>.</p>
<p data-start="3320" data-end="3392">On your <code data-start="3328" data-end="3343">services.html</code>, confirm you have BOTH of these near the bottom:</p>
