<h3 data-start="66" data-end="106">✅ Your JSON is currently <strong data-start="95" data-end="106">invalid</strong></h3>
<p data-start="107" data-end="216">In your first screenshot, right after the <code data-start="149" data-end="161">highlights</code> list ends, you have <strong data-start="182" data-end="215">extra closing brackets/braces</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="218" data-end="247">It looks like this (roughly):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="249" data-end="300"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼk">"highlights"</span><span>: [</span><br><span>  ...</span><br><span>]</span><br><span>]</span><br><span>},</span><br><span class="ͼk">"cards"</span><span>: [</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="302" data-end="406">That extra <code data-start="313" data-end="316">]</code> / <code data-start="319" data-end="322">}</code> breaks the JSON, so <code data-start="343" data-end="379">loadJSON("/content/services.json")</code> fails and nothing renders.</p>
<hr data-start="408" data-end="411">
<h2 data-start="413" data-end="468">Fix it by making the top structure exactly like this</h2>
<p data-start="470" data-end="543">Open <code data-start="475" data-end="498">content/services.json</code> and make sure it’s <strong data-start="518" data-end="529">exactly</strong> this pattern:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="545" data-end="2044"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span>  "intro": </span><span class="ͼk">"From MPI-accredited collision repair to mechanical work and glass, our team focuses on clean repairs, proper procedures, and quality control."</span><span>,</span><br><span>  "highlights": [</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Collision repair (MPI)"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Autobody Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Frame Straightening"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Paint &amp; Refinishing"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Mechanical Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Auto Glass Replacement"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics &amp; ADAS Scanning"</span><br><span>  ],</span><br><span>  "cards": [</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Collision Repair (MPI)"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"MPI accredited collision repairs restoring vehicles to manufacturer standards after accidents or damage."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Autobody Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Professional dent repair, panel replacement, and structural body repairs."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Frame Straightening"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Precision frame and structural alignment using professional frame straightening equipment."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Paint &amp; Refinishing"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"High-quality paint matching and refinishing for seamless factory-quality results."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Mechanical Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics and mechanical repairs including engine, suspension, and general vehicle maintenance."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Auto Glass Replacement"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Windshield and automotive glass replacement with proper sealing and installation."</span><br><span>    },</span><br><span>    {</span><br><span>      "title": </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics &amp; ADAS Scanning"</span><span>,</span><br><span>      "desc": </span><span class="ͼk">"Pre-scan and post-scan diagnostics including ADAS system calibration after repairs."</span><br><span>    }</span><br><span>  ]</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="2046" data-end="2063">The key part:</h3>
<p data-start="2064" data-end="2151">After the <code data-start="2074" data-end="2086">highlights</code> array closes, you should have <strong data-start="2117" data-end="2129">only one</strong> <code data-start="2130" data-end="2133">]</code> and then a comma:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2152" data-end="2177"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>],</span><br><span class="ͼk">"cards"</span><span>: [</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2179" data-end="2182">
<h2 data-start="2184" data-end="2208">After you save/commit</h2>
<ol data-start="2209" data-end="2544">
<li data-start="2209" data-end="2397">
<p data-start="2212" data-end="2261">Open this URL first to confirm the JSON is valid:</p>
<ul data-start="2265" data-end="2397">
<li data-start="2265" data-end="2312">
<p data-start="2267" data-end="2312"><code data-start="2267" data-end="2312">https://bevsrepair.ca/content/services.json</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2316" data-end="2397">
<p data-start="2318" data-end="2397">You should see the JSON nicely in the browser (not an error page / blank page).</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="2399" data-end="2544">
<p data-start="2402" data-end="2429">Then hard refresh services:</p>
<ul data-start="2433" data-end="2544">
<li data-start="2433" data-end="2455">
<p data-start="2435" data-end="2455"><strong data-start="2435" data-end="2455">Ctrl + Shift + R</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2459" data-end="2544">
<p data-start="2461" data-end="2544">Or open: <code data-start="2470" data-end="2511">https://bevsrepair.ca/services.html?v=1</code> (the <code data-start="2517" data-end="2523">?v=1</code> forces a fresh load)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="2546" data-end="2549">
