<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1280" data-end="1327"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://bevsrepair.ca/services.html?v=3</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1329" data-end="1332">
<h1 data-start="1334" data-end="1360">If everything is correct</h1>
<p data-start="1361" data-end="1430">You will immediately see <strong data-start="1386" data-end="1430">7 service cards appear under "Services".</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1432" data-end="1435">
<h3 data-start="1437" data-end="1529">Once this works, the next 3 upgrades will make the site look <strong data-start="1502" data-end="1528">much more professional</strong>:</h3>
<p data-start="1531" data-end="1663">1️⃣ <strong data-start="1535" data-end="1565">Shop hours + address block</strong><br data-start="1565" data-end="1568">
2️⃣ <strong data-start="1572" data-end="1595">Embedded Google Map</strong><br data-start="1595" data-end="1598">
3️⃣ <strong data-start="1602" data-end="1661">Online estimate upload (customers upload damage photos)</strong></p>
