s="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></span></button></div></div><div class="max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))]"></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="53ebd9f6-0fa0-4fcd-9c24-d91da5d6b04e" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="45">Yep — I can see the issue in your screenshot.</p>
<h3 data-start="47" data-end="65">✅ What’s wrong</h3>
<p data-start="66" data-end="144">Right after the <code data-start="82" data-end="94">highlights</code> list ends, you’ve got an <strong data-start="120" data-end="143">extra closing brace</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="146" data-end="175">It looks like this right now:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="177" data-end="311"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>  </span><span class="ͼk">"highlights"</span><span>: [</span><br><span>    ...</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics &amp; ADAS Scanning"</span><br><span>  ],</span><br><span>},          &lt;-- ❌ this extra } breaks the JSON</span><br><span class="ͼk">"cards"</span><span>: [</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="313" data-end="351">That <strong data-start="318" data-end="326"><code data-start="320" data-end="324">},</code></strong> should <strong data-start="334" data-end="341">not</strong> be there.</p>
<hr data-start="353" data-end="356">
<h2 data-start="358" data-end="366">✅ Fix</h2>
<p data-start="367" data-end="448">Make it look like this instead (no extra brace, just go straight into <code data-start="437" data-end="446">"cards"</code>):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="450" data-end="851"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span>  "intro": </span><span class="ͼk">"From MPI-accredited collision repair to mechanical work and glass, our team focuses on clean repairs, proper procedures, and quality control."</span><span>,</span><br><span>  "highlights": [</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Collision repair (MPI)"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Autobody Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Frame Straightening"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Paint &amp; Refinishing"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Mechanical Repair"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Auto Glass Replacement"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼk">"Diagnostics &amp; ADAS Scanning"</span><br><span>  ],</span><br><span>  "cards": [</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="853" data-end="884">What to do in GitHub editor</h3>
<ol data-start="885" data-end="1081">
<li data-start="885" data-end="946">
<p data-start="888" data-end="946">Find the line <strong data-start="902" data-end="925">right after the <code data-start="920" data-end="923">]</code></strong> that ends highlights</p>
</li>
<li data-start="947" data-end="974">
<p data-start="950" data-end="974"><strong data-start="950" data-end="974">Delete the <code data-start="963" data-end="967">},</code> line</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="975" data-end="1081">
<p data-start="978" data-end="1081">Make sure <code data-start="988" data-end="1000">"cards": [</code> is immediately after the highlights closing bracket with a comma like this: <code data-start="1077" data-end="1081">],</code></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1083" data-end="1086">
