<p data-start="107" data-end="147">So your <strong data-start="115" data-end="147">JSON structure is valid now.</strong></p>
<p data-start="149" data-end="220">However I see <strong data-start="163" data-end="181">one more issue</strong> that will stop the cards from showing.</p>
<hr data-start="222" data-end="225">
<h1 data-start="227" data-end="249">The real problem now</h1>
<p data-start="250" data-end="319">Your JavaScript expects the field name <strong data-start="289" data-end="299"><code data-start="291" data-end="297">desc</code></strong>, not <code data-start="305" data-end="318">description</code>.</p>
<p data-start="321" data-end="345">Earlier the code showed:</p>
