<p data-start="469" data-end="519">The <strong data-start="473" data-end="502">comma after the last item</strong> must be removed.</p>
<hr data-start="521" data-end="524">
<h1 data-start="526" data-end="531">Fix</h1>
<p data-start="533" data-end="545">Change this:</p>
