s:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" aria-pressed="false" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="cf48f4d3-c4f8-49ea-a134-2754f9f689e4" data-testid="conversation-turn-218" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div class="absolute flex h-8 w-3 origin-center items-center justify-center" style="opacity: 0; transform: scale(0);"><div class="bg-token-text-primary h-3 w-3 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="relative my-1 min-h-6"><div class="relative flex origin-top-left flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-clip rtl:origin-top-right" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="relative w-full text-start"><div class="flex w-full flex-row items-start justify-between gap-4 text-start"><button class="flex min-w-0 shrink-1 gap-0.5 items-center"><span class="font-medium w-full"><span class="flex gap-1 text-start align-middle items-center truncate text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary dark:text-[var(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)]" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="flex min-w-0 gap-1 items-center"><span class="min-w-0 truncate">Thought for 36s</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></span></button></div></div><div class="max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))]"></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="6715f0b9-a6cf-46b5-8e87-5556d7a6ec79" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="146">Ugh — I’m sorry. I know that “it <em data-start="33" data-end="41">should</em> work” feeling when you’ve done everything right and the page is still blank. Let’s get you unstuck fast.</p>
<p data-start="148" data-end="295">Based on your screenshots, your JSON looks <strong data-start="191" data-end="216">basically correct now</strong>. When it’s still blank after that, it’s almost always one of these two things:</p>
<h2 data-start="297" data-end="365">1) Your site is loading from a URL where <strong data-start="341" data-end="365">absolute paths break</strong></h2>
<p data-start="366" data-end="474">Your code uses paths that start with a <code data-start="405" data-end="408">/</code> (example: <code data-start="419" data-end="445">"/content/services.json"</code> and <code data-start="450" data-end="472">"/assets/js/site.js"</code>).</p>
<p data-start="476" data-end="580">That works <strong data-start="487" data-end="495">only</strong> when your site is truly served from the domain root (like <code data-start="554" data-end="578">https://bevsrepair.ca/</code>).</p>
<p data-start="582" data-end="679">But if you’re viewing it on the GitHub Pages default URL (project pages), it’s often served like:</p>
<ul data-start="681" data-end="743">
<li data-start="681" data-end="743">
<p data-start="683" data-end="743"><code data-start="683" data-end="743">https://bevsrepair.github.io/bevsrepair-site/services.html</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="745" data-end="806">In that case, a path like <code data-start="771" data-end="795">/content/services.json</code> points to:</p>
<ul data-start="808" data-end="873">
<li data-start="808" data-end="873">
<p data-start="810" data-end="873"><code data-start="810" data-end="862">https://bevsrepair.github.io/content/services.json</code>  ❌ (wrong)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="875" data-end="886">Instead of:</p>
<ul data-start="888" data-end="960">
<li data-start="888" data-end="960">
<p data-start="890" data-end="960"><code data-start="890" data-end="958">https://bevsrepair.github.io/bevsrepair-site/content/services.json</code> ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="962" data-end="1007">Fix (best fix — makes it work everywhere)</h3>
<p data-start="1008" data-end="1066">Change the paths to <strong data-start="1028" data-end="1040">relative</strong> (remove the leading <code data-start="1061" data-end="1064">/</code>).</p>
<h3 data-start="1068" data-end="1099">A) Edit <code data-start="1080" data-end="1099">assets/js/site.js</code></h3>
<p data-start="1100" data-end="1105">Find:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1106" data-end="1150"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼm">loadJSON</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼk">"/content/services.json"</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1151" data-end="1161">Change to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1162" data-end="1205"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼm">loadJSON</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼk">"content/services.json"</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1286">(And do the same for gallery/reviews/settings if they also have <code data-start="1271" data-end="1285">/content/...</code>)</p>
<h3 data-start="1288" data-end="1360">B) Edit ALL your HTML files (index/services/gallery/reviews/contact)</h3>
<p data-start="1361" data-end="1374">Change these:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1376" data-end="1529"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="Toggle view" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼo">&lt;link</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rel</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"stylesheet"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">href</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"/assets/css/styles.css"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">src</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"/assets/img/logo-placeholder.svg"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;script</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">src</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"/assets/js/site.js"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1531" data-end="1540">To these:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1542" data-end="1692"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="Toggle view" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Code" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="Preview" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼo">&lt;link</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rel</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"stylesheet"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">href</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"assets/css/styles.css"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">src</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"assets/img/logo-placeholder.svg"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;script</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">src</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"assets/js/site.js"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1694" data-end="1774">That one change fixes a <em data-start="1718" data-end="1723">ton</em> of “works here but not there” GitHub Pages issues.</p>
<hr data-start="1776" data-end="1779">
<h2 data-start="1781" data-end="1822">2) You’re seeing an old cached version</h2>
<p data-start="1823" data-end="1856">After you commit the fixes above:</p>
<ul data-start="1858" data-end="1978">
<li data-start="1858" data-end="1938">
<p data-start="1860" data-end="1938">Open: <code data-start="1866" data-end="1908">https://bevsrepair.ca/services.html?v=99</code> (change 99 to any new number)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1939" data-end="1978">
<p data-start="1941" data-end="1978">Or hard refresh: <strong data-start="1958" data-end="1978">Ctrl + Shift + R</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1980" data-end="1983">
<h2 data-start="1985" data-end="2022">Quick “proof” check (no dev tools)</h2>
<p data-start="2023" data-end="2075">After doing the path fix, open this in your browser:</p>
<ul data-start="2077" data-end="2124">
<li data-start="2077" data-end="2124">
<p data-start="2079" data-end="2124"><code data-start="2079" data-end="2124">https://bevsrepair.ca/content/services.json</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2126" data-end="2151">If that loads, then open:</p>
<ul data-start="2153" data-end="2196">
<li data-start="2153" data-end="2196">
<p data-start="2155" data-end="2196"><code data-start="2155" data-end="2196">https://bevsrepair.ca/assets/js/site.js</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2198" data-end="2254">If <strong data-start="2201" data-end="2211">either</strong> one fails (404), the page will stay blank.</p>
<hr data-start="2256" data-end="2259">
<p data-start="2261" data-end="2352">If you do the “remove the leading /” change, your Services cards should pop in immediately.</p>
<p data-start="2354" data-end="2597" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, tell me which address you’re testing right now (the <code data-start="2419" data-end="2434">bevsrepair.ca</code> one or the <code data-start="2446" data-end="2472">bevsrepair.github.io/...</code> one) and I’ll tell you <em data-start="2496" data-end="2505">exactly</em> which of the two issues it is — but honestly the relative-path fix solves both in one shot.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="