<hr data-start="2134" data-end="2137">
<h3 data-start="2139" data-end="2193">If Console shows <strong data-start="2160" data-end="2180">Unexpected token</strong> (JSON error)</h3>
<p data-start="2194" data-end="2320">Your JSON file has one small formatting issue (comma, quote, bracket). We’ll fix the exact character once you paste the error.</p>
<hr data-start="2322" data-end="2325">
<h3 data-start="2327" data-end="2369">If Console shows <strong data-start="2348" data-end="2369">.map of undefined</strong></h3>
<p data-start="2370" data-end="2470">That means the JS expects <code data-start="2396" data-end="2412">services.cards</code> but it’s missing or spelled differently.<br>
Your JS expects:</p>
<ul data-start="2471" data-end="2552">
<li data-start="2471" data-end="2480">
<p data-start="2473" data-end="2480"><code data-start="2473" data-end="2480">intro</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2481" data-end="2498">
<p data-start="2483" data-end="2498"><code data-start="2483" data-end="2490">cards</code> (array)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2499" data-end="2552">
<p data-start="2501" data-end="2552">inside each card: <code data-start="2519" data-end="2526">title</code>, <code data-start="2528" data-end="2534">desc</code>, optional <code data-start="2545" data-end="2552">items</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2554" data-end="2557">
