<hr data-start="939" data-end="942">
<h1 data-start="944" data-end="960">Why this works</h1>
<p data-start="961" data-end="983">Now the browser loads:</p>
<p data-start="985" data-end="1072">1️⃣ <code data-start="989" data-end="998">site.js</code><br data-start="998" data-end="1001">
2️⃣ Defines <code data-start="1013" data-end="1029">initServices()</code><br data-start="1029" data-end="1032">
3️⃣ Then your script runs and calls it</p>
<p data-start="1074" data-end="1114">So the function exists when it's called.</p>
<hr data-start="1116" data-end="1119">
<h1 data-start="1121" data-end="1142">After you change it</h1>
<ol data-start="1144" data-end="1217">
<li data-start="1144" data-end="1171">
<p data-start="1147" data-end="1171">Click <strong data-start="1153" data-end="1171">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1172" data-end="1200">
<p data-start="1175" data-end="1200">Wait about <strong data-start="1186" data-end="1200">10 seconds</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1201" data-end="1217">
<p data-start="1204" data-end="1217">Hard refresh:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1219" data-end="1243"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Ctrl + Shift + R</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
