<h1 data-start="463" data-end="499">Small improvement I recommend next</h1>
<p data-start="500" data-end="625">Right now the services are good, but we can make them <strong data-start="554" data-end="600">look a bit more professional for customers</strong> with one small addition.</p>
<p data-start="627" data-end="693">Under the intro text we can also show the <strong data-start="669" data-end="687">highlight list</strong> like:</p>
<p data-start="695" data-end="870">• Collision repair (MPI)<br data-start="719" data-end="722">
• Autobody repair<br data-start="739" data-end="742">
• Frame straightening<br data-start="763" data-end="766">
• Paint &amp; refinishing<br data-start="787" data-end="790">
• Mechanical repair<br data-start="809" data-end="812">
• Auto glass replacement<br data-start="836" data-end="839">
• Diagnostics &amp; ADAS scanning</p>
<p data-start="872" data-end="925">This makes it easier for customers scanning the page.</p>
<hr data-start="927" data-end="930">
<h1 data-start="932" data-end="976">The next 3 things I recommend for the site</h1>
<p data-start="977" data-end="1059">These will make it feel like a <strong data-start="1008" data-end="1036">real repair shop website</strong> instead of a template.</p>
<h3 data-start="1061" data-end="1109">1️⃣ Online estimate form with photo upload</h3>
<p data-start="1110" data-end="1152">Customers upload pictures of their damage.</p>
<h3 data-start="1154" data-end="1186">2️⃣ Google reviews section</h3>
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1214">Shows your shop reputation.</p>
<h3 data-start="1216" data-end="1248">3️⃣ Before / after gallery</h3>
<p data-start="1249" data-end="1281">This is huge for autobody shops.</p>
<hr data-start="1283" data-end="1286">
