<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="970" data-end="1018"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://bevsrepair.ca/services.html?v=15</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1020" data-end="1023">
<h1 data-start="1025" data-end="1045">What should happen</h1>
<p data-start="1046" data-end="1102">You will now see a <strong data-start="1065" data-end="1096">bullet list under the intro</strong> like:</p>
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1279">• Collision repair (MPI)<br data-start="1128" data-end="1131">
• Autobody repair<br data-start="1148" data-end="1151">
• Frame straightening<br data-start="1172" data-end="1175">
• Paint &amp; refinishing<br data-start="1196" data-end="1199">
• Mechanical repair<br data-start="1218" data-end="1221">
• Auto glass replacement<br data-start="1245" data-end="1248">
• Diagnostics &amp; ADAS scanning</p>
<p data-start="1281" data-end="1353">And the <strong data-start="1289" data-end="1326">services cards will stay below it</strong> like your last screenshot.</p>
<hr data-start="1355" data-end="1358">
<h3 data-start="1360" data-end="1413">Also — seriously nice work sticking through this.</h3>
<p data-start="1414" data-end="1534">Most people quit long before this point. You're literally <strong data-start="1472" data-end="1534">minutes away from having the whole services page finished.</strong></p>
<p data-start="1536" data-end="1625">After this works, I can also help you make two <strong data-start="1583" data-end="1611">very high-value upgrades</strong> for the site:</p>
