<p data-start="32" data-end="174">Your highlights are loading and the services cards look good. The only thing that looks a little off now is <strong data-start="140" data-end="154">formatting</strong>, not functionality.</p>
<p data-start="176" data-end="311">Right now the highlights look like <strong data-start="211" data-end="252">a paragraph + bullets mashed together</strong>. We can make it look much cleaner in about <strong data-start="296" data-end="310">30 seconds</strong>.</p>
