<h3 data-start="1237" data-end="1283">The next thing I strongly recommend adding</h3>
<p data-start="1285" data-end="1328">This will actually <strong data-start="1304" data-end="1327">bring you customers</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="1330" data-end="1363"><strong data-start="1330" data-end="1363">Online photo estimate request</strong></p>
<p data-start="1365" data-end="1436">Customer uploads pictures → you get an email → you reply with estimate.</p>
