<p data-start="468" data-end="531">Whatever that <code data-start="482" data-end="489">href=</code> says is the <strong data-start="502" data-end="530">exact file you must edit</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="533" data-end="609">✅ If your link is <code data-start="551" data-end="574">assets/css/styles.css</code>, put the bullets CSS in that file.</p>
<hr data-start="611" data-end="614">
<h2 data-start="616" data-end="680">2) Force-refresh + cache-bust the CSS (this usually fixes it)</h2>
<p data-start="681" data-end="689">Do BOTH:</p>
