The reason the list didn't change is because <strong data-start="117" data-end="157">the CSS rule isn't strong enough yet</strong>, so the page’s existing styles are overriding it.</p>
<p data-start="209" data-end="252">We’ll fix it with a slightly stronger rule.</p>
<hr data-start="254" data-end="257">
<h1 data-start="259" data-end="290">Step 1 — Open this file again</h1>
<p data-start="291" data-end="301">In GitHub:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="303" data-end="332"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/css/styles.css</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="334" data-end="364">Scroll to the <strong data-start="348" data-end="363">very bottom</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="366" data-end="401">Replace the bullets code with this:</p>
