<p data-start="204" data-end="340">Let’s make it wrap into <strong data-start="228" data-end="252">2 columns on desktop</strong>, and fall back to <strong data-start="271" data-end="293">1 column on mobile</strong>, plus tighten the spacing so it looks cleaner.</p>
<h2 data-start="342" data-end="405">Do this in <code data-start="356" data-end="379">assets/css/styles.css</code> (near the bottom is fine)</h2>
<p data-start="407" data-end="429">Add/replace with this:</p>
