<hr data-start="1035" data-end="1038">
<h3 data-start="1040" data-end="1071">If it STILL stays 1 column…</h3>
<p data-start="1072" data-end="1346" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">That means the <code data-start="1087" data-end="1093">&lt;ul&gt;</code> isn’t wide enough (inside a container). In that case we’ll make the highlight “card” full width.<br data-start="1190" data-end="1193">
