ain:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="247edfda-cfed-4c90-b1be-f4e07703974d" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="104">Great choice — <strong data-start="15" data-end="57">pill tags will look cleaner and modern</strong>, and they’re easier than the column layout. 👍</p>
<p data-start="106" data-end="152">We’ll turn the services into little tags like:</p>
<p data-start="154" data-end="283"><code data-start="154" data-end="169">MPI Collision</code> <code data-start="170" data-end="187">Autobody Repair</code> <code data-start="188" data-end="209">Frame Straightening</code> <code data-start="210" data-end="231">Paint &amp; Refinishing</code> <code data-start="232" data-end="251">Mechanical Repair</code> <code data-start="252" data-end="264">Auto Glass</code> <code data-start="265" data-end="283">ADAS Diagnostics</code></p>
<hr data-start="285" data-end="288">
<h1 data-start="290" data-end="315">Step 1 — Update the CSS</h1>
<p data-start="317" data-end="322">Open:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="324" data-end="353"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>assets/css/styles.css</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="355" data-end="400">Scroll to the <strong data-start="369" data-end="384">very bottom</strong> and paste this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="402" data-end="738"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼe">/* Services highlight pills */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">bullets</span><span> {</span><br><span>  display: </span><span class="ͼj">flex</span><span>;</span><br><span>  flex-wrap: </span><span class="ͼj">wrap</span><span>;</span><br><span>  gap: </span><span class="ͼj">8</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  margin-top: </span><span class="ͼj">12</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  padding-left: </span><span class="ͼj">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>  list-style: </span><span class="ͼj">none</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼl">bullets</span><span> </span><span class="ͼo">li</span><span> {</span><br><span>  background: </span><span class="ͼg">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼj">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">255</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼj">0.08</span><span>);</span><br><span>  border: </span><span class="ͼj">1</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">solid</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">var</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">--line</span><span>);</span><br><span>  border-radius: </span><span class="ͼj">999</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  padding: </span><span class="ͼj">6</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">12</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  font-size: </span><span class="ͼj">13</span><span class="ͼg">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  white-space: </span><span class="ͼj">nowrap</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="740" data-end="755">Commit changes.</p>
