<p data-start="36" data-end="117">A nicer homepage will make the whole site feel more finished even without photos.</p>
<p data-start="119" data-end="155">The best homepage upgrades next are:</p>
<ol data-start="157" data-end="305">
<li data-start="157" data-end="189">
<p data-start="160" data-end="189">make the top section stronger</p>
</li>
<li data-start="190" data-end="230">
<p data-start="193" data-end="230">add a cleaner “why choose us” section</p>
</li>
<li data-start="231" data-end="265">
<p data-start="234" data-end="265">add a proper contact/info block</p>
</li>
<li data-start="266" data-end="305">
<p data-start="269" data-end="305">make the call-to-action more obvious</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="307" data-end="348">Here’s what I’d suggest for Bev’s Repair.</p>
<h2 data-start="350" data-end="376">Best homepage structure</h2>
<p data-start="378" data-end="389">At the top:</p>
<ul data-start="390" data-end="507">
<li data-start="390" data-end="407">
<p data-start="392" data-end="407">Strong headline</p>
</li>
<li data-start="408" data-end="440">
<p data-start="410" data-end="440">Short trust-building paragraph</p>
</li>
<li data-start="441" data-end="458">
<p data-start="443" data-end="458">Call Now button</p>
</li>
<li data-start="459" data-end="482">
<p data-start="461" data-end="482">Get Directions button</p>
</li>
<li data-start="483" data-end="507">
<p data-start="485" data-end="507">Request a Quote button</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="509" data-end="520">Then below:</p>
<ul data-start="521" data-end="623">
<li data-start="521" data-end="551">
<p data-start="523" data-end="551">Small service highlight tags</p>
</li>
<li data-start="552" data-end="587">
<p data-start="554" data-end="587">Why customers choose Bev’s Repair</p>
</li>
<li data-start="588" data-end="605">
<p data-start="590" data-end="605">Contact + hours</p>
</li>
<li data-start="606" data-end="623">
<p data-start="608" data-end="623">Reviews preview</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 data-start="625" data-end="651">Better homepage wording</h2>
<p data-start="653" data-end="680">For the main headline, use:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="682" data-end="762"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href