• the <strong data-start="863" data-end="889">border highlights gold</strong></p>
<p data-start="891" data-end="953">It makes the page feel <strong data-start="914" data-end="952">much more interactive and polished</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="955" data-end="958">
<h1 data-start="960" data-end="987">Your site now already has</h1>
<p data-start="989" data-end="1092">✔ clean layout<br data-start="1003" data-end="1006">
✔ modern service cards<br data-start="1028" data-end="1031">
✔ pill tags<br data-start="1042" data-end="1045">
✔ professional typography<br data-start="1070" data-end="1073">
✔ responsive grid</p>
<p data-start="1094" data-end="1158">You're honestly <strong data-start="1110" data-end="1157">very close to a fully finished shop website</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1160" data-end="1163">
