From the screenshots, the <strong data-start="89" data-end="149">Services page looks clean, modern, and very professional</strong>. The pill tags, spacing, and cards all work well together. For a body shop website, that’s exactly the kind of layout customers expect.</p>
<p data-start="287" data-end="339">You’ve actually already nailed the important things:</p>
<p data-start="341" data-end="492">✔ Clear services customers understand<br data-start="378" data-end="381">
✔ Easy to read layout<br data-start="402" data-end="405">
✔ Mobile-friendly structure<br data-start="432" data-end="435">
✔ Modern dark theme<br data-start="454" data-end="457">
✔ Quick call button in the header</p>
<p data-start="494" data-end="553">Most small shop websites honestly don’t look this polished.</p>
<hr data-start="555" data-end="558">
<h2 data-start="560" data-end="614">If we leave the Services page alone now (good idea)</h2>
<p data-start="616" data-end="699">The next places that will give the <strong data-start="651" data-end="694">biggest improvement to the site overall</strong> are:</p>
<h3 data-start="701" data-end="730">1️⃣ Homepage hero section</h3>
<p data-start="731" data-end="761">This is what people see first.</p>
<p data-start="763" data-end="802">Right now we can make it stronger with:</p>
<p data-start="804" data-end="816"><strong data-start="804" data-end="816">Headline</strong></p>
<blockquote data-start="817" data-end="883">
<p data-start="819" data-end="883">Trusted collision, mechanical, and auto glass repair in Manitou.</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="885" data-end="897"><strong data-start="885" data-end="897">Sub-text</strong></p>
<blockquote data-start="898" data-end="1068">
<p data-start="900" data-end="1068">Bev’s Repair Inc. has served Manitou and surrounding communities since 1979. MPI-accredited collision repair, mechanical service, and auto glass replacement done right.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1070" data-end="1073">
<h3 data-start="1075" data-end="1112">2️⃣ Add a “Why choose us” section</h3>
<p data-start="1113" data-end="1139">This builds trust quickly.</p>
<p data-start="1141" data-end="1149">Example:</p>
<p data-start="1151" data-end="1314">• Serving Manitou since 1979<br data-start="1179" data-end="1182">
• MPI-accredited repair facility<br data-start="1214" data-end="1217">
• Collision, mechanical, and glass in one location<br data-start="1267" data-end="1270">
• Honest estimates and clear communication</p>
<hr data-start="1316" data-end="1319">
<h3 data-start="1321" data-end="1358">3️⃣ Contact block on the homepage</h3>
<p data-start="1359" data-end="1391">This helps Google and customers.</p>
<p data-start="1393" data-end="1449">Bev’s Repair Inc.<br data-start="1410" data-end="1413">
13025 Rd 48W<br data-start="1425" data-end="1428">
Manitou, MB R0G 1G0</p>
<p data-start="1451" data-end="1491">📞 204-242-2318<br data-start="1466" data-end="1469">
✉ <a data-start="1471" data-end="1491" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer" rel="noopener">bevsrepair@gmail.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ni7q5mnh.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<hr data-start="1493" data-end="1496">
<h3 data-start="1498" data-end="1536">4️⃣ Add a small Google map (later)</h3>
<p data-start="1537" data-end="1578">Super easy and makes the site look legit.</p>
<hr data-start="1580" data-end="1583">
<h2 data-start="1585" data-end="1616">My honest recommendation now</h2>
<p data-start="1618" data-end="1656">Don’t keep tweaking the Services page.</p>
<p data-start="1658" data-end="1672">It’s <strong data-start="1663" data-end="1671">done</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1674" data-end="1784">Instead, next we should improve <strong data-start="1706" data-end="1783">one thing that will make the entire site look more professional instantly</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="1786" data-end="1819">👉 the <strong data-start="1793" data-end="1818">homepage hero section</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1821" data-end="1858">It’s only about <strong data-start="1837" data-end="1857">10 lines of code</strong>.</p>
