<h1 data-start="1084" data-end="1100">What this adds</h1>
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1160">You’ll now see a small badge above the headline that says:</p>
<p data-start="1162" data-end="1213"><strong data-start="1162" data-end="1213">Serving Manitou &amp; surrounding area • Since 1979</strong></p>
<p data-start="1215" data-end="1276">This gives the homepage a <strong data-start="1241" data-end="1275">more professional hero section</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1278" data-end="1281">
<p data-start="1283" data-end="1522" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">After this, the <strong data-start="1299" data-end="1367">next improvement will make the homepage look dramatically better</strong>:<br data-start="1368" data-end="1371">
